'''凯瑟琳·伊丽莎白·哈德森'''（{{lang-en|Katheryn Elizabeth Hudson}}，{{bd|1984年|10月25日}}），以其藝名'''凱蒂·佩芮'''（{{lang-en|Katy Perry}}）聞名，是一名美國歌手、詞曲作家及電視節目-{zh-hans:评审; zh-hant:評審}-。小時候在教堂唱歌後，身為青少年的她在福音音樂領域追尋職業生涯。
2001年，派瑞与[[潘普林音樂|红山唱片]]签约，并发布其首张录音室专辑《[[凯蒂·哈德森_(专辑)|凯蒂·哈德森]]》，但专辑在商业上不成功。次年红山唱片倒闭，她搬到[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]冒险闯入世俗音乐领域，并开始与制作人{{le|格倫·巴拉德|Glen Ballard}}、[[卢克博士|卢克博士]]和[[马克斯·马丁|马克斯·马丁]]合作。被{{le|岛屿好果酱音乐集团|Island Def Jam Music Group}}和[[哥伦比亚唱片|哥伦比亚唱片]]抛弃后，2007年4月派瑞与[[国会唱片|国会唱片]]签署{{le|唱片合约|Recording contract}}。2008年6月派瑞凭借其[[流行摇滚|流行摇滚]]风格的第二张专辑《[[花漾派对|花漾派对]]》的单曲《[[忽冷忽热|忽冷忽热]]》和引发争议的同性恋主题单曲《[[亲了一个拉拉|亲了一个拉拉]]》一炮而红。她的第三张专辑《[[花漾年华|花漾年华]]》闯入[[迪斯科|迪斯科]]领域，派生出美国[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]]榜首单曲《[[加州女孩|加州女孩]]》、《[[烟火_(歌曲)|烟火]]》、《[[外星品种|外星品种]]》和《[[惡搞週末|惡搞週末]]》，此外还有第三名单曲《[[离开的人是你|离开的人是你]]》。2012年3月，她发行再版专辑《[[花漾年华：甜心全记录|花漾年华：甜心全记录]]》，派生出单曲《[[做自己_(單曲)|做自己]]》和《[[绝对清醒|绝对清醒]]》。其第四张专辑《[[棱镜_(专辑)|棱镜]]》2013年发布，受到流行乐和舞曲影响。她成为首位在[[Vevo|Vevo]]上有多部录影带播放量达到10亿的女歌手，其中歌曲《[[聽我吼|聽我吼]]》、《[[黑马_(歌曲)|黑马]]》的录影带均获得超过20亿的点击量。而在《烟火》和《聽我吼》等歌曲中，她强调了自强和自尊的主题。派瑞以古怪和本着搞笑的个人衣着风格而知名，她的时装结合了鲜艳的颜色和食物主题。她的演唱会设有精心设计的舞台和服装。2020年8月28日，《微笑》正式發布。

派瑞获得过[[凯蒂·派瑞奖项及提名列表|众多奖项]]，包括四个[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]，并在2011年到2015年被《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志列入“音乐界最赚钱的女性”榜单。纵观她的职业生涯，她在全球卖出了4000万张专辑和1.25億首单曲，是[[畅销音乐艺人列表|史上作品销量最多的音乐人之一]]。派瑞还为众多[[证言法|产品代言]]，并发布香水{{le|Purr|Purr by Katy Perry}}、{{le|Meow!|Meow! by Katy Perry}}、{{le|杀手女王|Killer Queen by Katy Perry}}和{{le|瘋狂藥水|Mad Potion}}。而在影视作品方面，她在2012年7月发布自传纪录片《[[凯蒂佩芮：做自己|凯蒂佩芮：做自己]]》，并帮2012年的《[[藍色小精靈|藍色小精靈]]》和[[蓝色小精灵2|其在2013年的续集]]裏的角色配音。

== 生平与生涯 ==
=== 1984-1998年：早年生活 ===
凯瑟琳·伊丽莎白·哈德逊出生于[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[圣巴巴拉_(加利福尼亚州)|圣巴巴拉]]戈列塔河谷小屋醫院{{sfn|Perry|2012|loc=05:23|ref=movie}}<ref>https://www.noozhawk.com/noozhawk/print/081511_jeff_moehlis_katy_perry_at_santa_barbara_bowl</ref><ref name="Friedlander 2012 15">{{harvnb|Friedlander|2012|p=15}}</ref>，父亲莫里斯·基思·哈德逊（{{lang|en|Maurice Keith Hudson}}）和母亲玛丽·克丽斯蒂·派瑞（{{lang|en|Mary Christine Perry}}）是[[五旬节运动|五旬节运动]]牧师。她的父母都[[生_(基督教)|生为基督徒]]，在度过“狂野的青春”后信奉上帝<ref name="GraffBold">{{cite news|url=http://thescotsman.scotsman.com/features/Interview-Katy-Perry--Hot.4988069.jp|title=Interview: Katy Perry – Hot N Bold|last=Graff|first=Gary|date=2009-02-21|newspaper=The Scotsman|accessdate=2009-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090307025809/http://thescotsman.scotsman.com/features/Interview-Katy-Perry--Hot.4988069.jp|archive-date=2009-03-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。派瑞拥有葡萄牙、德国、爱尔兰和英国血统<ref>{{harvnb|Cowlin|2014|pp=11; 51}}</ref>。在母親家族方面，她是电影导演、制片人{{le|弗兰克·派瑞|Frank Perry}}的侄女<ref>{{cite journal|last=Robinson|first=Lisa|title=Katy Perry's Grand Tour|magazine=Vanity Fair|date=2011-05-03|accessdate=2015-10-17|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/features/2011/06/katy-perry-full-201106|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025031343/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/features/2011/06/katy-perry-full-201106|archivedate=2014-10-25|journal=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的弟弟大卫是歌手<ref>{{cite journal|title=7 Questions With David Hudson: His Movement, The Music & Advice From Big Sister Katy Perry|url=http://www.spin.com/articles/katy-perrys-little-brother-hudson-to-you-video/|magazine=Spin|first=Chris|last=Martins|accessdate=2014-04-30|date=2012-09-04|journal=|archive-date=2014-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502002326/http://www.spin.com/articles/katy-perrys-little-brother-hudson-to-you-video/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，姐姐叫安琪拉<ref>{{harvnb|Friedlander|2012|p=7}}</ref>。3岁到11岁时，派瑞经常辗转全国各地，跟随父母创办教会，直至再次在圣芭芭拉安家。成长的过程中，她就读于宗教学校和夏令营学校，包括在[[小学|小学]]时期就读的加利福尼亚圣巴巴拉基督教学校（{{lang|en|Santa Barbara Christian School}}）和[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]天堂谷基督教学校（{{lang|en|Paradise Valley Christian School}}）<ref name="Friedlander 2012 15"/><ref>{{cite news|last=Masley|first=Ed|title=Katy Perry talks Super Bowl, Scottsdale childhood|url=http://www.azcentral.com/story/entertainment/music/2015/01/09/interview-katy-perry-talks-super-bowl-halftime-show/21497063/|accessdate=2015-01-09|newspaper=The Arizona Republic|date=2015-01-09}}</ref>。她的家人曾陷入经济困境<ref name="GQ">{{cite journal|last=Wallace|first=Amy|title=Katy Perry's GQ Cover Story|url=http://www.gq.com/women/photos/201402/katy-perry-cover-story-february-2014|magazine=GQ|date=2014-01-19|accessdate=2014-02-06|journal=|archive-date=2014-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140207095700/http://www.gq.com/women/photos/201402/katy-perry-cover-story-february-2014|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾有一段日子靠[[美國補充營養協助計畫|食物券]]和父母教会供给信众的食物仓库储备维生<ref name=RS2010>{{cite journal|first=Vanessa|last=Grigoriadis|title=Sex, God & Katy Perry|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/sex-god-katy-perry-rolling-stones-2010-cover-story-20110607|magazine=Rolling Stone|date=2010-08-19|accessdate=2014-05-20|journal=|archive-date=2017-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171113112853/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/sex-god-katy-perry-rolling-stones-2010-cover-story-20110607|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在成长的过程中，派瑞和她的兄弟姐妹们不被允许吃{{le|幸运护身符|Lucky Charms}}麦片，因为“幸运”一词让他们的母亲想起[[路西法|路西法]]，但母亲却把[[恶魔蛋|恶魔蛋]]称为“天使蛋”<ref>{{harvnb|Hudson|2012|p=27}}</ref>。小派瑞主要听[[福音音乐|福音音乐]]<ref name="MontgomeryGospel">{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1589848/katy-perry-dishes-on-her-long-and-winding-road-from-singing-gospel-to-kissing-girls/|title=Katy Perry Dishes on Her 'Long And Winding Road' From Singing Gospel To Kissing Girls|last=Montgomery|first=James|date=2008-06-24|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2009-02-15|archive-date=2017-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170716163244/http://www.mtv.com/news/1589848/katy-perry-dishes-on-her-long-and-winding-road-from-singing-gospel-to-kissing-girls/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因为在家里听世俗音乐通常会被家人劝阻。她透过从朋友家偷来的几张[[CD|CD]]发现了流行乐<ref name=Childhood>{{cite journal|title=Katy Perry Discusses Evangelical Childhood, Term 'Deviled Eggs' Banned from House|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/471742/katy-perry-discusses-evangelical-childhood-term-deviled-eggs-banned-from-house|magazine=Billboard|date=2011-05-04|accessdate=2014-02-06|journal=|archive-date=2017-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707162610/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/471742/katy-perry-discusses-evangelical-childhood-term-deviled-eggs-banned-from-house|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管不严格定义为教徒，但派瑞曾表示：“我无时不刻都在祈祷——为了自控，为了谦卑<ref name=Marie>{{cite journal|last=Hoffman|first=Claire|title=Katy Conquers All|url=http://www.marieclaire.com/celebrity-lifestyle/celebrities/katy-perry-feature-katheryn-hudson|magazine=Marie Claire|date=2013-12-09|accessdate=2013-12-10|journal=|archive-date=2013-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212083655/http://www.marieclaire.com/celebrity-lifestyle/celebrities/katy-perry-feature-katheryn-hudson|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”追随姐姐安琪拉，佩里利用她姐姐的录影带开始学习唱歌。她在父母面前表演了歌曲，父母还以为她上过声乐课。9岁时，她开始接受{{le|声乐教学|Vocal pedagogy|训练}}<ref>{{harvnb|Friedlander|2012|p=8}}</ref>，参加父母的神职工作<ref name="GraffBold"/>，9岁到17岁时在教会唱歌<ref>{{harvnb|Hudson|2012|p=41}}</ref>。13岁时，派瑞收到她作为生日礼物的第一把吉他<ref name="GraffBold"/><ref>{{harvnb|Friedlander|2012|p=18}}</ref>，并公开表演她写的歌曲。她在长大时“成为一名非常像的传统加州女孩”，青少年时她开始学滑旱冰、滑滑板、冲浪。大卫形容她在青春期时是一个“[[假小子|假小子]]”<ref>{{harvnb|Hudson|2012|p=25}}</ref>。她还参加舞蹈课程，学跳[[摇摆舞|摇摆舞]]、[[林迪舞|林迪舞]]和{{le|吉特布格舞|Jitterbug}}<ref>{{harvnb|Summers|2012|p=37}}</ref>。

=== 1999-2006年：事业起步 ===
高一那年<ref name="Elle">{{cite journal|last=Hudson|first=Kathryn|title=Katy Perry: Elle Canada Interview|url=http://www.ellecanada.com/celebrity/celebrity-spotlight/katy-perry-elle-canada-interview/a/77774|magazine=ELLE|date=2013-08-29|accessdate=2014-02-06|journal=|archive-date=2014-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223130310/http://www.ellecanada.com/celebrity/celebrity-spotlight/katy-perry-elle-canada-interview/a/77774|dead-url=no}}</ref>，15岁的派瑞达到了[[普通教育发展证书|普通教育发展证书]]要求，离开{{le|道斯梯形城堡高中|Dos Pueblos High School}}追寻音乐生涯。她曾有一段日子在圣巴巴拉{{le|西方音乐学院|Music Academy of the West}}学习[[意大利歌剧|意大利歌剧]]。她的歌声吸引[[田纳西州|田纳西州]][[纳什维尔|纳什维尔]]摇滚艺人史蒂夫·托马斯（{{lang|en|Steve Thomas}}）和{{le|詹妮弗·克纳普|Jennifer Knapp}}的关注，两人曾把她带到那儿提升她的创作水平<ref>{{harvnb|Hudson|2012|p=37}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.glamour.com/magazine/2010/01/katy-perry-she-kisses-boys-too|magazine=Glamour|accessdate=2014-08-09|first=Amy|last=Spencer|title=Katy Perry (she kisses boys, too!)|date=2010-01-06|journal=|archive-date=2014-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811093304/http://www.glamour.com/magazine/2010/01/katy-perry-she-kisses-boys-too|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在纳什维尔，她开始录制[[样本唱片|样本唱片]]，学习写歌和弹吉他<ref name="MontgomeryGospel"/>。与[[红山唱片|红山唱片]]签约后，派瑞录制她的首支专辑——名为《[[凯蒂·哈德森_(专辑)|凯蒂·哈德森]]》的福音唱片。专辑于2001年3月6日发行<ref>{{harvnb|Friedlander|2012|p=24}}</ref>，她加盟奇怪得正常巡演（{{lang|en|The Strangely Normal Tour}}）以宣传专辑<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.westhartfordnews.com/articles/2011/12/08/entertainment/doc4eddc976cee14391469110.txt |title=Phil Joel to play in West Hartford |newspaper=West Hartford News |date=2011-12-08 |accessdate=2014-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908064802/http://www.westhartfordnews.com/articles/2011/12/08/entertainment/doc4eddc976cee14391469110.txt |archive-date=2014-09-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。尽管只卖出大约200张<ref>{{harvnb|Summers|2012|pp=10–11}}</ref>，在商业上没有获得成功，但专辑还是获得乐评人的积极评价。同年12月，派瑞与厂牌解约<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=JRIEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA10&lpg=PA10&dq=Doors+close+in+Pamplin%27s+beleaguered+music+division&source=bl&ots=IhkgAzjV_f&sig=oVhjB0Tfm7TTig91O3tbF3zM7Eo&hl=en&sa=X&ei=j67hU6yOAZCOyATQuoCADQ&ved=0CC0Q6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=Doors%20close%20in%20Pamplin%27s%20beleaguered%20music%20division&f=false|magazine=Billboard|date=2001-12-01|accessdate=2014-08-06|title=Doors close in Pamplin's beleaguered music division|first=Deborah Evans|last=Price|journal=|archive-date=2015-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150319012909/http://books.google.com/books?id=JRIEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA10&lpg=PA10&dq=Doors+close+in+Pamplin%27s+beleaguered+music+division&source=bl&ots=IhkgAzjV_f&sig=oVhjB0Tfm7TTig91O3tbF3zM7Eo&hl=en&sa=X&ei=j67hU6yOAZCOyATQuoCADQ&ved=0CC0Q6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=Doors%20close%20in%20Pamplin%27s%20beleaguered%20music%20division&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

从福音音乐过渡到世俗音乐，派瑞17岁时移居[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]<ref name=WMag>{{cite journal |last=Hirschberg |first=Lynn |title=Katy Perry |url=http://www.wmagazine.com/people/celebrities/2013/10/katy-perry-prism-interview/ |magazine=W |date=2013-10-22 |accessdate=2013-10-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025215605/http://www.wmagazine.com/people/celebrities/2013/10/katy-perry-prism-interview/ |archivedate=2013-10-25 |journal= }}</ref>，开始跟制作人{{le|格伦·巴拉德|Glen Ballard}}写歌{{sfn|Perry|2012|loc = 21:11|ref=movie}}。

2003年，为了避免与女演员[[凯特·哈德森|凯特·哈德森]]混淆，她一度以凯瑟琳·派瑞的艺名进行表演。后来她用上母亲的娘家姓，取艺名凯蒂·派瑞{{sfn|Perry|2012|loc=38:33|ref=movie}}。

2004年，派瑞签约巴拉德的唱片公司、当时隶属于{{le|岛屿好果酱音乐集团|The Island Def Jam Music Group}}的Java。她开始创作独唱专辑，但在Java每况日下后，专辑被搁置<ref name="glen ballard billboard">{{cite journal|last1=Conniff|first1=Tamara|title=I've Stopped Asking for Permission . I'd Rather Ask for Forgiveness.|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1BMEAAAAMBAJ&pg=RA1-PA76&dq=java+katy+perry&hl=en&sa=X&ei=9sw7VZyJFcOYgwS6-YGwBQ&ved=0CE8Q6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=java%20katy%20perry&f=false|accessdate=2015-04-25|magazine=Billboard|date=2004-12-25|journal=|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906163754/https://books.google.com/books?id=1BMEAAAAMBAJ&pg=RA1-PA76&dq=java+katy+perry&hl=en&sa=X&ei=9sw7VZyJFcOYgwS6-YGwBQ&ved=0CE8Q6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=java%20katy%20perry&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巴拉德后来把派瑞介绍给[[哥伦比亚唱片|哥伦比亚唱片]][[A&R|艺人培训]]主管{{le|蒂姆·迪瓦恩|Tim Devine}}，她被签约为独唱艺人。在接下来的两年内，派瑞为她在哥伦比亚的处女作创作录制素材，并与{{le|戴斯蒙·柴德|Desmond Child}}、{{le|格雷格·威尔斯|Greg Wells}}、{{le|巴奇·沃克|Butch Walker}}、斯科特·卡特勒/安妮·普列文（{{lang|en|Scott Cutler/Anne Previn}}）、{{le|黑客帝国三人组|The Matrix (production team)}}、[[凯拉·狄奥果笛|凯拉·狄奥果笛]]、[[马克斯·马丁|马克斯·马丁]]和[[卢克博士|卢克博士]]等词曲作者共事<ref name="Anokute Hit Quarters">{{cite journal|last1=Blumenrath|first1=Jan|title=Interview with Chris Anokute|url=http://www.hitquarters.com/index.php3?page=intrview/2010/October18_4_57_7.html|accessdate=2015-04-25|publisher=HitQuarters|date=2010-10-18|journal=|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417201326/http://www.hitquarters.com/index.php3?page=intrview%2F2010%2FOctober18_4_57_7.html|archive-date=2015-04-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="billboard long">{{cite news|title=Katy Perry Cover Story|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=WWxbO-SGG7AC&pg=RA4-PA19&dq=katy+perry+met+dr+luke&hl=en&sa=X&ei=CbA7VcLILMOiNqDugIgH&ved=0CEMQ6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=katy%20perry%20met%20dr%20luke&f=false|accessdate=2015-04-25|magazine=Billboard|date=2010-07-03|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906160038/https://books.google.com/books?id=WWxbO-SGG7AC&pg=RA4-PA19&dq=katy+perry+met+dr+luke&hl=en&sa=X&ei=CbA7VcLILMOiNqDugIgH&ved=0CEMQ6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=katy%20perry%20met%20dr%20luke&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，迪瓦恩建议他们组成“真正的乐团”后，她与黑客帝国三人组录制唱片<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hochman|first1=Steve|title=Making a production of it|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2004/feb/15/entertainment/ca-popeye15|accessdate=2015-04-25|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=2004-02-15|archive-date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610181224/http://articles.latimes.com/2004/feb/15/entertainment/ca-popeye15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派瑞在专辑几近完成时于2006年离开哥伦比亚，之后在独立艺人培训公司{{le|出租车音乐|TAXI (A&R)}}工作<ref>{{harvnb|Summers|2012|pp=11–12}}</ref>。

派瑞在正式出道前有过小成功。在她与巴拉德创作的专辑中，歌曲《简单就好》（{{lang|en|''Simple''}}）出现在2005年电影《{{le|牛仔裤的夏天|The Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants (film)}}》的原声带中<ref name=Summers>{{harvnb|Summers|2012|p=11}}</ref>。她还给[[米克·贾格尔|米克·贾格尔]]的歌曲《{{le|秉性难移|Old Habits Die Hard}}》作伴唱<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/people/2013/10/31/mick-jagger-says-he-never-hit-on-katy-perry-at-18/3327313/|title=Mick Jagger says he never hit on 18-year-old Katy Perry|newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|accessdate=2013-10-31|date=2013-10-31|archive-date=2013-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101035902/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/people/2013/10/31/mick-jagger-says-he-never-hit-on-katy-perry-at-18/3327313/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，该曲赢得[[第62届金球奖|2005年金球奖最佳原创歌曲奖]]<ref>{{cite journal|title='Alfie', 'Aviator', and 'Ray' Rack Up Awards|magazine=Billboard|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=ZxQEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA11|accessdate=2014-04-24|date=2005-01-29|first=Carla|last=Hay|journal=|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709031124/http://books.google.com/books?id=ZxQEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2004年9月，《{{le|搅拌机 (杂志)|Blender (magazine)|搅拌机}}》杂志将派瑞提名为“明日之星”（{{lang|en|The Next Big Thing}}）<ref name=Summers/>。2006年，她为[[P.O.D|花钱找死乐团]]单曲《告别现在》（{{lang|en|''Goodbye for Now''}}）录制伴唱，并在歌曲音乐录影带的结尾处亮相。那一年，派瑞还亮相{{le|碳叶子|Carbon Leaf}}歌曲《学会飞》（{{lang|en|''Learn to Fly''}}）的音乐录影带，还在时任男友、{{le|体育课英雄|Gym Class Heroes}}主唱[[崔维·麦考伊|崔维·麦考伊]]乐队的歌曲《丘比特被扼颈》（{{lang|en|Cupid's Chokehold}}）的音乐录影带中扮演崔维的情人<ref>{{harvnb|Summers|2012|p=12}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Rosen|first=Craig|title=Katy Perry's Best Moments Undercover|url=https://music.yahoo.com/blogs/stop-the-presses/katy-perry-best-moments-undercover-150523486.html|publisher=Yahoo! Music|accessdate=2014-08-22|date=2013-10-18|archive-date=2014-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102050029/https://music.yahoo.com/blogs/stop-the-presses/katy-perry-best-moments-undercover-150523486.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{harvnb|Friedlander|2012|p=46}}</ref>。

=== 2007-2009年：《花漾派對》与事业突破 ===
[[File:Katy_Perry_performing.jpg|缩略图]]

哥伦比亚抛弃派瑞后，时任公司宣传主任的{{le|安赫丽卡·库伯-伯勒尔|Angelica Cob-Baehler}}将派瑞的试样给了[[维珍唱片|维珍唱片]]主席{{le|杰森·弗洛姆|Jason Flom}}。弗洛姆确信她会是突出的明星，她在2007年4月签约[[国会唱片|国会唱片]]。公司安排他与卢克博士共事，为的是在她现有的素材中加上一段“不可否认的伟大音乐”<ref name="hitquarters">{{cite web |url=http://www.hitquarters.com/index.php3?page=intrview/opar/intrview_AnokuteCorrection.html |title=Correction to the interview with Chris Anokute |publisher=HitQuarters |date=2011-01-21 |accessdate=2014-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713071228/http://www.hitquarters.com/index.php3?page=intrview%2Fopar%2Fintrview_AnokuteCorrection.html |archive-date=2014-07-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Mervis|first1=Scott|title=Katy Perry's star keeps rising|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/music/2014/07/22/Katy-Perry-s-star-keeps-rising/stories/201407210006|newspaper=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette|date=2014-07-21|accessdate=2014-07-31|archive-date=2014-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723153416/http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/music/2014/07/22/Katy-Perry-s-star-keeps-rising/stories/201407210006|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派瑞和卢克博士共同为她的第二张专辑《[[花漾派对|花漾派对]]》创作歌曲《[[亲了一个拉拉|亲了一个拉拉]]》和《[[忽冷忽热|忽冷忽热]]》。随着2007年11月《[[你好Gay|你好Gay]]》MV的发行，宣传活动宣告拉开帷幕<ref>{{harvnb|Friedlander|2012|pp=58; 61}}</ref>。随后主打《[[你好Gay|你好Gay]]》的[[迷你专辑|迷你专辑]]被发行，用来创造收益<ref name="GraffBold" /><ref name="hitquarters.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.hitquarters.com/index.php3?page=intrview/opar/intrview_Chris_Anokute_Interview.html |title=Interview With Chris Anokute |publisher=HitQuarters |date=2010-10-18 |accessdate=2014-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713070818/http://www.hitquarters.com/index.php3?page=intrview%2Fopar%2Fintrview_Chris_Anokute_Interview.html |archive-date=2014-07-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[麦当娜|麦当娜]]于2008年4月在电台节目《约翰杰伊与里奇》（{{lang|en|''JohnJay & Rich''}}）中称赞该歌曲<ref>{{harvnb|Summers|2012|pp=38–39}}</ref>，称它是她“最喜欢的歌曲”，从而帮助宣传<ref>{{harvnb|Friedlander|2012|p=61}}</ref>。2008年3月，派瑞在《{{le|青春野火 (电视剧)|Wildfire (TV series)|青春野火}}》的《生命太短暂》（{{lang|en|Life's Too Short}}）一集中客串扮演一名酒吧歌手<ref>{{harvnb|Summers|2012|p=61}}</ref>，6月份在《{{le|不安分的青春|The Young and the Restless}}》的节目杂志《骚动族范儿》（{{lang|en|''Restless Style''}}）的照片摄影中本色出演<ref>{{harvnb|Summers|2012|p=99}}</ref>。

2008年4月28日，派瑞与国会唱片发行了她的首支单曲《亲了一个拉拉》<ref>{{cite journal|title=I Kissed a Girl|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/pictures/katy-perrys-20-biggest-hits-20140730/1-i-kissed-a-girl-0160167|accessdate=2014-10-24|magazine=Rolling Stone|date=2014-07-30|journal=|archive-date=2014-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108160532/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/pictures/katy-perrys-20-biggest-hits-20140730/1-i-kissed-a-girl-0160167|dead-url=no}}</ref>，作为《花漾派对》的主打歌。首个接纳该首歌的电台是[[纳什维尔|纳什维尔]]的{{le|WRVW|WRVW}}，播放该曲的头三天，他们收到大量热情的点歌请求<ref name="hitquarters.com"/>。该曲在[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]]上位列榜首<ref>{{cite journal|last=Cohen|first=Jonathan|title=Rihanna Topples Katy Perry on Hot 100|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1044448/rihanna-topples-katy-perry-on-hot-100|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2014-03-15|date=2008-08-14|journal=|archive-date=2015-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114143039/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1044448/rihanna-topples-katy-perry-on-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>。专辑于6月17日发行，获得褒贬不一的专业评价，并在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]上位列第九<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/artists/perrykaty/oneoftheboys|title=One of the Boys|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2009-03-06|archive-date=2009-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090227060410/http://www.metacritic.com/music/artists/perrykaty/oneoftheboys|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/305595/katy-perry/chart?sort=timeon&f=305|title=Katy Perry – Chart history: Billboard 200|accessdate=2009-03-02|magazine=Billboard|journal=|archive-date=2014-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713083438/http://www.billboard.com/artist/305595/katy-perry/chart?sort=timeon&f=305|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。《忽冷忽热》在9月发布<ref>{{cite journal|title=Hot n Cold|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/pictures/katy-perrys-20-biggest-hits-20140730/11-hot-n-cold-0068249|accessdate=2014-10-24|magazine=Rolling Stone|date=2014-07-30|journal=|archive-date=2014-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108092428/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/pictures/katy-perrys-20-biggest-hits-20140730/11-hot-n-cold-0068249|dead-url=no}}</ref>，成为专辑第二首取得成功的单曲，在公告牌百强榜上位列第三<ref name=Hot100History>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/305595/Katy%2BPerry/chart?f=379|title=Katy Perry – Chart history: The Hot 100|accessdate=2014-06-24|magazine=Billboard|journal=|archive-date=2015-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150516113917/http://www.billboard.com/artist/305595/Katy%20Perry/chart?f=379|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，同时在德国<ref>{{cite web |url=http://musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/title/Perry%2C+Katy/Hot+n+Cold/single |title=Hot n Cold (Single) |publisher=Musicline |accessdate=2014-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714190034/http://musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/title/Perry%2C%2BKaty/Hot%2Bn%2BCold/single |archive-date=2014-07-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、加拿大<ref name=CanadaCharts>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/305595/Katy%2BPerry/chart?f=793|title=Katy Perry – Chart history: Billboard Canadian Hot 100|accessdate=2014-06-26|magazine=Billboard|journal=|archive-date=2014-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221214633/http://www.billboard.com/artist/305595/Katy%20Perry/chart?f=793|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、荷兰<ref>{{cite web|title=Nederlandse Top 40 – week 01, 2009|url=http://www.top40.nl/top40/2009/week-01|publisher=Dutch Top 40|accessdate=2014-07-27|archive-date=2015-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723064903/http://www.top40.nl/top40/2009/week-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>和奥地利的榜单上位列榜首<ref>{{cite web|title=Katy Perry — Hot N Cold|url=http://www.austriancharts.at/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy+Perry&titel=Hot+n+Cold&cat=s|publisher=Ö3 Austria Top 40|accessdate=2014-07-27|archive-date=2015-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151227182739/http://austriancharts.at/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy+Perry&titel=Hot+N+Cold&cat=s|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后的单曲《[[想著你|想著你]]》和《[[在赌城醒来|在赌城醒来]]》在2009年发布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gfa.radioandrecords.com/publishGFA/GFANextPage.asp?sDate=01/12/2009&Format=1 |title=CHR/Top 40 |publisher=Radio & Records |date=2009-01-12 |accessdate=2014-04-16 |first=Kevin |last=Carter |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605132643/http://gfa.radioandrecords.com/publishGFA/GFANextPage.asp?sDate=01%2F12%2F2009&Format=1 |archivedate=2013-06-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Waking Up in Vegas|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/pictures/katy-perrys-20-biggest-hits-20140730/13-waking-up-in-vegas-0994169|accessdate=2014-10-21|magazine=Rolling Stone|date=2014-07-30|journal=|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022092138/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/pictures/katy-perrys-20-biggest-hits-20140730/13-waking-up-in-vegas-0994169|dead-url=no}}</ref>，均在[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]]跻身30强<ref name=Hot100History />。派瑞2004年和黑客帝国三人组一起录制的乐队同名处女作专辑，于2009年1月27日在[[iTunes|iTunes]]发行，这是她单飞成功的结果<ref name="KaufmanMatrix">{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1603622/the-matrix-drop-long-lost-album-featuring-katy-perry/|title=The Matrix Drop Long-Lost Album Featuring Katy Perry|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|date=2009-01-27|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2014-04-29|archive-date=2015-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151027032958/http://www.mtv.com/news/1603622/the-matrix-drop-long-lost-album-featuring-katy-perry/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2008年，完成[[Warped巡迴|Warped巡迴]]之后<ref>{{cite journal|title=Katy Perry on Warped 2008: Mosh Pits, Injuries and Andrew WK|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/katy-perry-on-warped-2008-mosh-pits-injuries-and-andrew-wk-20080825|magazine=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2014-04-03|date=2008-08-25|journal=|archive-date=2017-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171113113225/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/katy-perry-on-warped-2008-mosh-pits-injuries-and-andrew-wk-20080825|dead-url=no}}</ref>，派瑞于同年11月主持了[[2008年MTV欧洲音乐大奖|2008年MTV欧洲音乐大奖]]，在那里她获得{{le|MTV欧洲音乐大奖最佳新人奖|MTV Europe Music Award for Best New Act|最佳新人奖}}<ref>{{cite news|title=Americans Katy Perry, Britney Spears, Kanye West, 30 Seconds To Mars Dominate 2008 MTV EMAs|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1598808/mtv-europe-music-awards-dominated-by-americans.jhtml|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|publisher=MTV News|date=2008-11-07|accessdate=2015-09-13|archive-date=2013-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213203433/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1598808/mtv-europe-music-awards-dominated-by-americans.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年1月到11月，她开启个人首个领衔世界巡演“[[你好凯蒂巡演|你好凯蒂巡演]]”，来支持《花漾派對》<ref name=Hudson83>{{harvnb|Hudson|2012|p=83}}</ref>。2009年8月4日，她在[[不要怀疑|不要怀疑]]的{{le|不要怀疑2009年夏日巡演|No Doubt 2009 Summer Tour|2009年夏季巡演}}做开场表演<ref>{{cite news|title=Last Night: No Doubt, Katy Perry, the Sounds at Verizon Wireless Amphitheater|first=Albert|last=Ching|url=http://blogs.ocweekly.com/heardmentality/2009/08/last_night_no_doubt_katy_perry.php|newspaper=OC Weekly|date=2009-08-05|accessdate=2014-05-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140521110545/http://blogs.ocweekly.com/heardmentality/2009/08/last_night_no_doubt_katy_perry.php|archivedate=2014-05-21}}</ref>。2009年11月，派瑞主持了[[2009年MTV欧洲音乐大奖|2009年MTV欧洲音乐大奖]]，成为连续主持两届典礼的第一人<ref>{{cite news|title=MTV EMAs Host Katy Perry Brings 'Cabaret' To Berlin|publisher=MTV|date=2009-10-01|url=http://www.mtv.com.au/kings-of-leon/news/katy-perry-to-host-emas|accessdate=2015-09-13|archive-date=2017-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170713094029/http://www.mtv.com.au/kings-of-leon/news/katy-perry-to-host-emas|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2009年7月22日，派瑞录制现场专辑《[[原音重現_(凱蒂·佩芮專輯)|原音重现]]》，包括《花漾派對》其中五首单曲的不插电版，以及两首新歌《Brick By Brick》和《Hackensack》<ref name="UnpluggedNotes">{{cite AV media notes |title=MTV Unplugged |others=Katy Perry |year=2009 |type=Compact Disc |publisher=Capitol Records }}</ref>。专辑同年11月17日发行<ref name="MTV Unplugged Album">{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1623630/katy-perrys-mtv-unplugged-album-will-feature-two-new-songs/|title=Katy Perry's ''MTV Unplugged'' Album Will Feature Two New Songs|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2014-04-28|date=2009-10-12|first=James|last=Montgomery|archive-date=2017-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171024033050/http://www.mtv.com/news/1623630/katy-perrys-mtv-unplugged-album-will-feature-two-new-songs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派瑞还和其他艺人出过两首单曲：一首是在2009年9月与[[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]]乐团[[3OH!3|3OH!3]]合作的混音歌曲《[[追星族_(歌曲)|追星族]]》<ref>{{cite web|title=Starstrukk (feat. Katy Perry)|url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/starstrukk-feat.-katy-perry/id330823124|publisher=iTunes Store|date=2009-09-14|accessdate=2014-07-23|archive-date=2015-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724115223/https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/starstrukk-feat.-katy-perry/id330823124|dead-url=no}}</ref>；另一首则是在2010年1月与[[提姆巴蘭|提姆巴蘭]]的合唱曲《[[如果我们再相遇|如果我们再相遇]]》，出自他的专辑《[[超级惊选2|超级惊选2]]》<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/pictures/katy-perrys-20-biggest-hits-20140730/18-if-we-ever-meet-again-timbaland-feat-katy-perry-0617558|title=If We Ever Meet Again|magazine=Rolling Stone|date=2014-07-30|accessdate=2014-11-02|journal=|archive-date=2017-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171113060306/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/pictures/katy-perrys-20-biggest-hits-20140730/18-if-we-ever-meet-again-timbaland-feat-katy-perry-0617558|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.rap-up.com/2010/01/18/video-timbaland-f-katy-perry-if-we-ever-meet-again/#more-36245 |title=Video: Timbaland f/ Katy Perry – 'If We Ever Meet Again' |magazine=Rap-Up |date=2010-01-08 |accessdate=2010-08-02 |journal= |archive-date=2014-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009022310/http://www.rap-up.com/2010/01/18/video-timbaland-f-katy-perry-if-we-ever-meet-again/#more-36245 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[吉尼斯世界记录|吉尼斯世界记录]]》2010年版因其卖出200万份数字单曲，而承认她创下了「女歌手在美国数字排行榜上最好开局」记录（{{lang|en|Best Start on the US Digital Chart by a Female Artist}}）<ref name=Guinness2010>{{harvnb|Glenday|2010|p=405}}</ref>。

《[[亲了一个拉拉|亲了一个拉拉]]》引起宗教团体和[[LGBT|LGBT]]团体的争论。前者批评它有关于同性恋的主题，而后者控诉她用[[双性恋|双性恋]]出售唱片。为了回应外界对她父母反对她的音乐作品和事业的猜测，派瑞告诉MTV他们并没有因为她的成功而跟她闹矛盾<ref name="VenaRumors">{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1593166/katy-perry-responds-rumors-parents-criticism.jhtml|title=Katy Perry Responds To Rumors of Parents' Criticism: 'They Love And Support Me'|last=Vena|first=Jocelyn|date=2008-08-20|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2014-04-29|archive-date=2013-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213203136/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1593166/katy-perry-responds-rumors-parents-criticism.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年12月与[[崔维·麦考伊|崔维·麦考伊]]分手后<ref name="TravieSplit">{{cite news|title=Katy Perry And Travis Split|url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/katy-perry/news/katy-perry-and-travis-split|publisher=MTV News|date=2009-01-05|accessdate=2014-04-29|archive-date=2017-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170704043930/http://www.mtv.co.uk/katy-perry/news/katy-perry-and-travis-split|dead-url=no}}</ref>，她在2009年夏天客串《[[大明星小跟班|大明星小跟班]]》时，遇到了她未来的老公[[羅素·布蘭德|羅素·布蘭德]]。她的镜头包括两场吻戏，都没出现在戏里面<ref name=GreekExplain>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1640830/katy-perry-explains-why-she-was-cut-from-get-him-to-the-greek/|title=Katy Perry Explains Why She Was Cut From 'Get Him to the Greek'|publisher=MTV News|first=Jocelyn|last=Vena|date=2010-06-04|accessdate=2012-02-18|archive-date=2017-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025022244/http://www.mtv.com/news/1640830/katy-perry-explains-why-she-was-cut-from-get-him-to-the-greek/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派瑞在[[2009年MTV音乐录影带大奖|2009年MTV音乐录影带大奖]]上再次遇见罗素后，她开始跟罗素约会<ref name=RussellDating>{{cite web |last=Ziegbe |first=Mawuse |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1647232/katy-perry-russell-brands-love-story-began-at-the-vmas/ |title=Katy Perry, Russell Brand's Love Story Began at the VMAs |publisher=MTV News |date=2010-09-04 |accessdate=2010-11-09 |archive-date=2015-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151104100511/http://www.mtv.com/news/1647232/katy-perry-russell-brands-love-story-began-at-the-vmas/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年12月31日，两人在印度[[拉贾斯坦邦|拉贾斯坦邦]]度假时订婚<ref name=Engaged>{{cite web|last=Heldman|first=Breanne L.|title=Katy Perry and Russell Brand Engaged in India|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/160483/katy-perry-and-russell-brand-engaged-in-india|publisher=E!|accessdate=2010-01-06|date=2010-01-06|archive-date=2015-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151104100513/http://www.eonline.com/news/160483/katy-perry-and-russell-brand-engaged-in-india|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 2010-2012年：《花漾年华 (Teenage Dream)》和婚姻 ===
出任《[[美国偶像|美国偶像]]》嘉宾评委后<ref>{{cite journal|last=Barrett|first=Annie|title='American Idol': The Kara vs. Katy Lifetime movie|url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2010/01/27/american-idol-the-kara-vs-katy-perry-lifetime-movie/|magazine=Entertainment Weekly|date=2010-01-27|accessdate=2014-04-29|journal=|archive-date=2014-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112055719/http://popwatch.ew.com/2010/01/27/american-idol-the-kara-vs-katy-perry-lifetime-movie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，派瑞于2010年5月7日发布了《[[加州女孩|加州女孩]]》，该曲由说唱歌手[[史努比狗狗|史努比狗狗]]客串<ref>{{cite news|last=Montgomery|first=James|title=Katy Perry Debuts New Single 'California Gurls'|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1638711/katy-perry-debuts-new-single-california-gurls/|accessdate=2014-09-21|publisher=MTV News|date=2010-05-07|archive-date=2014-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140912002221/http://www.mtv.com/news/1638711/katy-perry-debuts-new-single-california-gurls/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该曲是她的第三张录音室专辑《[[花漾年华|花漾年华]]》的主打单曲，6月份在公告牌百强单曲榜上斩获冠军<ref>{{cite news|last=Montgomery|first=James|title=Katy Perry's 'California Gurls' Makes History in Rise To #1|publisher=MTV News|date=2010-06-09|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1641186/katy-perrys-california-gurls-makes-history-in-rise-to-1/|accessdate=2014-04-28|archive-date=2014-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502061315/http://www.mtv.com/news/1641186/katy-perrys-california-gurls-makes-history-in-rise-to-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|first=Gary|last=Trust|title=Katy Perry Speeds To No. 1 on Hot 100|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/957858/katy-perry-speeds-to-no-1-on-hot-100|magazine=Billboard|date=2010-06-09|accessdate=2010-06-09|journal=|archive-date=2013-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508095943/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/957858/katy-perry-speeds-to-no-1-on-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她还在当月晚些时候在《[[英国版X音素|英国版X音素]]》担任评委<ref name="XFactorJudge">{{cite web|title=Katy Perry Hits Dublin For X Factor Auditions|url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/x-factor/228776-katy-perry-cheryl-cole-x-factor|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2010-06-28|date=2010-06-28|archive-date=2013-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017142034/http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/x-factor/228776-katy-perry-cheryl-cole-x-factor|dead-url=no}}</ref>，之后又于7月发布专辑的第二首单曲《[[花漾年华_(歌曲)|花漾年华]]》<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2010/07/22/katy-perryteenage-dream-new-single/|title=Katy Perry's new single 'Teenage Dream' hits the web|last=Greenblatt|first=Leah|date=2010-07-22|magazine=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=2014-09-21|journal=|archive-date=2014-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109002349/http://music-mix.ew.com/2010/07/22/katy-perryteenage-dream-new-single/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《花漾年华》9月份在《公告牌》位居榜首<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Pietroluongo|first1=Silvio|title=Katy Perry's 'Teenage Dream' Dethrones Eminem on Hot 100|magazine=Billboard|date=2010-09-08|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/956446/katy-perrys-teenage-dream-dethrones-eminem-on-hot-100|accessdate=2014-07-31|journal=|archive-date=2014-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908070757/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/956446/katy-perrys-teenage-dream-dethrones-eminem-on-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>。专辑于2010年8月24日发行<ref>{{cite news|last=Vena|first=Jocelyn|title=Katy Perry To Release Teenage Dream On August 24|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1638865/katy-perry-to-release-teenage-dream-on-august-24/|accessdate=2014-09-10|publisher=MTV News|date=2010-05-11|archive-date=2014-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140911052754/http://www.mtv.com/news/1638865/katy-perry-to-release-teenage-dream-on-august-24/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以第一位的成绩首次亮相公告牌二百强单曲榜<ref>{{cite journal|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|title=Katy Perry's 'Prism' Set for No. 1 Debut on Billboard 200 Chart|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/digital-and-mobile/5763267/katy-perrys-prism-set-for-no-1-debut-on-billboard-200|magazine=Billboard|date=2013-10-23|accessdate=2014-03-15|journal=|archive-date=2014-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220195810/http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/digital-and-mobile/5763267/katy-perrys-prism-set-for-no-1-debut-on-billboard-200|dead-url=no}}</ref>。乐评人对专辑的评价褒贬不一<ref>{{cite web|title=Teenage Dream Reviews|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/teenage-dream|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2014-03-15|archive-date=2014-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424065201/http://www.metacritic.com/music/teenage-dream|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但它在全球已卖出570万张<ref name="Patricia Reaney">{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/22/entertainment-us-katyperry-prism-idUSBRE99L0P920131022|title=Katy Perry shows vulnerability, maturity on new album 'Prism'|first=Patricia|last=Reaney|agency=Reuters|date=2013-10-22|accessdate=2014-06-03|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626155151/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/22/entertainment-us-katyperry-prism-idUSBRE99L0P920131022|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。10月，《[[烟火_(歌曲)|烟火]]》作为专辑第三首单曲被发布<ref>{{cite news|last1=Semigran|first1=Aly|title=Glee Sets 'Firework' Apart From 'Silly Love Songs'|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1657508/glee-sets-firework-apart-from-silly-love-songs/|accessdate=2014-09-21|publisher=MTV News|date=2011-02-08|archive-date=2014-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205043148/http://www.mtv.com/news/1657508/glee-sets-firework-apart-from-silly-love-songs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该曲于2010年12月8日成为专辑连续第三首百强榜冠军曲<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/949557/katy-perrys-firework-shines-over-hot-100|title=Katy Perry's 'Firework' Shines Over Hot 100|work=Billboard|first=Silvio|last=Pietroluongo|date=2010-12-08|accessdate=2010-12-08|journal=|archive-date=2013-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130212162311/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/949557/katy-perrys-firework-shines-over-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>，还在美国获得[[音乐唱片销量认证|9张铂金唱片销量认证]]<ref name=TopCertified>{{cite web|title=RIAA Crowns Katy Perry Top Certified Digital Artist Ever|url=http://www.riaa.com/newsitem.php?content_selector=newsandviews&news_month_filter=6&news_year_filter=2014&id=8F0AFFDA-2B31-72D3-0590-6944C8F0DB00|publisher=Recording Industry Association of America|accessdate=2014-06-26|date=2014-06-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714100511/http://www.riaa.com/newsitem.php?content_selector=newsandviews&news_year_filter=2014&id=8F0AFFDA-2B31-72D3-0590-6944C8F0DB00&news_month_filter=6|archivedate=2014-07-14}}</ref>。

由说唱歌手[[肯伊·威斯特|肯伊·威斯特]]客串的《[[外星品种|外星品种]]》于2011年2月16日作为专辑的第四首单曲发布<ref>{{cite journal|last=Wete|first=Brad|title=Kanye West abducts Katy Perry on singer's new single, 'E.T'|url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2011/02/16/kanye-west-katy-perry-et/|accessdate=2014-09-21|magazine=Entertainment Weekly|date=2011-02-16|journal=|archive-date=2014-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014085217/http://music-mix.ew.com/2011/02/16/kanye-west-katy-perry-et/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该曲在五个非连续周称霸百强榜，使得专辑成为历史上第九张在百强榜上产出四首榜首单曲的专辑<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/472289/katy-perrys-et-rockets-to-no-1-on-hot-100|title=Katy Perry's 'E.T.' Rockets To No. 1 on Hot 100|magazine=Billboard|first=Gary|last=Trust|date=2011-03-30|accessdate=2011-03-30|journal=|archive-date=2013-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508071128/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/472289/katy-perrys-et-rockets-to-no-1-on-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>。接着《[[恶搞週末|恶搞週末]]》于6月成为第五首单曲<ref>{{cite journal |title=FMQB: Radio Industry News, Music Industry Updates, Nielsen Ratings, Music News and more! |magazine=FMQB |date=2011-06-06 |url=http://www.fmqb.com/Article.asp?id=69239 |accessdate=2014-09-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5rQQuV2wk?url=http://www.fmqb.com/Article.asp?id=69239 |archivedate=2010-07-23 |journal= }}</ref>，而派瑞随着8月17日该曲称霸单曲榜，成为首位同一专辑有五首百强榜榜首单曲的女艺人，也是继[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔·杰克逊]]的专辑《[[Bad_(迈克尔·杰克逊专辑)|Bad]]》的第二位艺人<ref name=TieMichael>{{cite journal|last=Trust|first=Gary|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/467879/katy-perry-makes-hot-100-history-ties-michael-jacksons-record|title=Katy Perry Makes Hot 100 History: Ties Michael Jackson's Record|magazine=Billboard|date=2011-08-17|accessdate=2011-08-17|journal=|archive-date=2013-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130330234333/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/467879/katy-perry-makes-hot-100-history-ties-michael-jacksons-record|dead-url=no}}</ref>。凭借这张专辑，她在2011年1月的[[2011年全美音乐奖|全美音乐奖]]上赢得一项荣誉奖<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Nordyke|first1=Kimberly|title=AMAs 2011: Katy Perry Surprised With Special Achievement Award|magazine=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2011-11-20|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/amas-american-music-awards-winners-katy-perry-264203|accessdate=2015-11-15|journal=|archive-date=2016-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160217221240/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/amas-american-music-awards-winners-katy-perry-264203|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并在2013年创下一项吉尼斯世界纪录<ref name=Guinness2013>{{harvnb|Glenday|2013|p=423}}</ref>。9月7日，她创下了连续69周位列百强榜前十的首位女艺人的纪录<ref name="adeles-someone">{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/467566/adeles-someone-like-you-soars-to-no-1-on-hot-100|magazine=Billboard|title=Adele's 'Someone Like You' Soars To No. 1 on Hot 100|first=Gary|last=Trust|date=2011-09-07|accessdate=2011-09-07|journal=|archive-date=2011-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110729050908/http://www.billboard.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月，《[[离开的人是你|离开的人是你]]》作为第六首单曲发布<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.fmqb.com/Article.asp?id=16687 |title=Available for Airplay (10/11) |magazine=FMQB |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/62Jk8gp91?url=http://www.fmqb.com/Article.asp?id=16687 |archivedate=2011-10-10 |accessdate=2014-09-22 |deadurl=yes |journal= }}</ref>。歌曲在百强榜上名列第三<ref name=BiggestBillboard>{{cite journal|last=Lipshutz|first=Jason|title=Katy Perry's 10 Biggest Billboard Hits|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5645538/katy-perrys-10-biggest-billboard-hits|accessdate=2014-10-21|magazine=Billboard|date=2013-08-09|journal=|archive-date=2014-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011204318/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5645538/katy-perrys-10-biggest-billboard-hits|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，在加拿大名列第二<ref name=CanadaCharts/>。2012年2月13日，国会唱片发行了《[[花漾年华：甜心全记录|花漾年华：甜心全记录]]》的主打单曲《[[做自己_(单曲)|做自己]]》，该曲在百强榜夺冠，总体上成为派瑞第七首在该榜夺冠的单曲<ref name=Hot100History/><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/506206/katy-perrys-part-of-me-hits-itunes-radio-monday|title=Katy Perry's' 'Part of Me' Hits iTunes, Radio Monday|magazine=Billboard|date=2012-02-11|last=Trust|first=Gary|accessdate=2014-04-29|journal=|archive-date=2014-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429023848/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/506206/katy-perrys-part-of-me-hits-itunes-radio-monday|dead-url=no}}</ref>。专辑于3月23日发布<ref>{{cite web|title=Teenage Dream: The Complete Confection|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/teenage-dream-complete-confection/id716084282|publisher=iTunes Store|accessdate=2014-07-31|date=2012-03-23|archive-date=2015-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211231242/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/teenage-dream-complete-confection/id716084282|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[绝对清醒|绝对清醒]]》作为第二首再版单曲，于5月22日发布，在百强榜上最高排在第二位<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yOHDLK8b?url=http://www.allaccess.com/top40-mainstream/future-releases |url=http://www.allaccess.com/top40-mainstream/future-releases |title=Top 40/M Future Releases |publisher=All Access |archivedate=2011-05-02 |accessdate=2014-09-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>(peaking at number two on the Hot 100)<ref name=BiggestBillboard/>，并在加拿大<ref name=CanadaCharts/>和新西兰斩获冠军<ref>{{cite web|title=Katy Perry — Wide Awake|url=http://www.charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy+Perry&titel=Wide+Awake&cat=s|publisher=Top 40 Singles|accessdate=2014-07-31|archive-date=2015-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150831034425/http://charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Katy+Perry&titel=Wide+Awake&cat=s|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1月5日，{{le|尼尔森唱片市场调查公司|Nielsen SoundScan}}表示，她凭借着3760万份的销量，成为了美国数字销量第六高的艺人<ref>{{cite web|title=The Nielsen Company & Billboard's 2011 Music Industry Report|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20120105005547/en/Nielsen-Company-Billboard%E2%80%99s-2011-Music-Industry-Report|publisher=Business Wire|first=Anna|last=Loynes|accessdate=2012-01-05|archive-date=2012-01-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/64TshZep3?url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20120105005547/en/Nielsen-Company-Billboard%E2%80%99s-2011-Music-Industry-Report|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当月，她成为了首位有四首数字销量超过500万份的女艺人<ref>{{cite web |last=Grein |first=Paul |url=https://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/week-ending-jan-15-2012-songs-song-won-012657212.html |title=Week Ending Jan. 15, 2012. Songs: The Song That Won't Drop |publisher=Yahoo! Music |date=2012-01-19 |accessdate=2014-04-29 |archive-date=2014-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009073310/https://music.yahoo.com/blogs/chart-watch/week-ending-jan-15-2012-songs-song-won-012657212.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

