派瑞于2011年2月和2012年1月开启了她的第二个巡演{{le|加州之梦世界巡回演唱会|California Dreams Tour}}<ref name=Hudson83/>，以支持《花漾年华》<ref name=TourBegin>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5793234/katy-perry-announces-first-prismatic-world-tour-dates|title=Katy Perry Announces First 'PRISMATIC' World Tour Dates|date=2013-11-18|magazine=Billboard|first=Jason|last=Lipshutz|accessdate=2014-04-29|journal=|archive-date=2014-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220201032/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5793234/katy-perry-announces-first-prismatic-world-tour-dates|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巡演在全球赚到5900万美元的票房<ref name="psp">{{cite journal |url=http://www.pollstarpro.com/charts/2011YearEndTop25WorldwideTours.pdf |title=Top 25 Worldwide Tours (01/01/2011 – 12/31/2011) |date=2011-12-28 |format=PDF |magazine=Pollstar |accessdate=2011-12-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/64I05wGYs?url=http://www.pollstarpro.com/charts/2011YearEndTop25WorldwideTours.pdf |archivedate=2011-12-29 |journal= }}</ref>，为她在[[2011年MTV欧洲音乐大奖|2011年MTV欧洲音乐大奖]]上赢得最佳现场表演奖<ref>{{cite news|last1=Vena|first1=Jocelyn|title=Justin Bieber Parties With Selena Gomez, LMFAO After MTV EMA|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1673836/ema-parties-justin-bieber/|accessdate=2015-09-13|publisher=MTV News|date=2011-11-07|archive-date=2016-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160125154146/http://www.mtv.com/news/1673836/ema-parties-justin-bieber/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年9月23日，她在2011年{{le|里约摇滚音乐节|Rock in Rio}}的开幕日与[[艾尔顿·约翰|艾尔顿·约翰]]、{{le|克劳迪娅·莱蒂|Claudia Leitte}}和[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]共同表演<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jcnet.com.br/noticias.php?codigo=221209|title=Rock in Rio 2011: A hora e a vez do pop|newspaper=Jornal da Cidade de Bauru|accessdate=2011-11-05|date=2011-09-26|language=pt|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111011172544/http://www.jcnet.com.br/noticias.php?codigo=221209|archive-date=2011-10-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2010年9月，派瑞预计亮相第41季的《[[芝麻街|芝麻街]]》。她的镜头被上传到[[YouTube|YouTube]]后，观众批评派瑞暴露[[乳沟|乳沟]]。节目正式播出四天前，{{le|芝麻街工作室|Sesame Workshop}}宣布该片段不会在电视上播放，但仍可以在网络上观看<ref>{{cite news|first=Michael|last=Getler|title=Was This Show a Must or a Bust(ier)?|url=http://www.pbs.org/ombudsman/2010/09/was_this_show_a_must_or_a_bustier.html|publisher=PBS|date=2010-09-24|accessdate=2014-11-27|archive-date=2015-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150502071759/http://www.pbs.org/ombudsman/2010/09/was_this_show_a_must_or_a_bustier.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派瑞随后在《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》拿这个争议开玩笑，她在节目中担任音乐嘉宾，还在一个小品中穿上露出大部分乳沟的[[艾蒙|艾蒙]]主题衬衣<ref>{{cite web|title=Katy Perry mocks Sesame Street ban|url=http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/katy-perry/videos/hot-n-cold-sesame-street/|publisher=Capital FM|accessdate=2014-01-14|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906165303/http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/katy-perry/videos/hot-n-cold-sesame-street/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年12月，派瑞在《[[辛普森一家|辛普森一家]]》圣诞节特别剧集《{{le|大战平安夜|The Fight Before Christmas}}》真人片段中扮演[[莫·希斯拉克|莫·希斯拉克]]的女友<ref name=Kaufman>{{cite news|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|title=Katy Perry to appear on 'The Simpsons' in December|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1648733/katy-perry-appear-on-simpsons-december.jhtml|accessdate=2011-08-19|date=2010-09-27|publisher=MTV News|archive-date=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107195937/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1648733/katy-perry-appear-on-simpsons-december.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Snierson|first=Dan|title=Katy Perry to guest star on 'The Simpsons'! Here's your exclusive first look|magazine=Entertainment Weekly|date=2010-09-25|url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2010/09/25/katy-perry-the-simpsons-exclusive/|accessdate=2014-11-27|journal=|archive-date=2014-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205121538/http://popwatch.ew.com/2010/09/25/katy-perry-the-simpsons-exclusive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年2月，她在《[[老爸老妈的浪漫史|老爸老妈的浪漫史]]》《{{le|噢，亨妮|Oh Honey}}》一集中扮演名为亨妮的女性<ref>{{cite web |last=Tucker |first=Ken |url=http://watching-tv.ew.com/2011/02/07/how-i-met-your-mother-katy-perry/ |title=How I Met Your Mother: 'Oh Honey' |magazine=Entertainment Weekly |date=2011-02-07 |accessdate=2011-08-27 |archive-date=2014-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141225005729/http://watching-tv.ew.com/2011/02/07/how-i-met-your-mother-katy-perry/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这个角色让她在2012年1月赢得了{{le|第38届人民选择奖|38th People's Choice Awards|最受欢迎电视客串明星}}奖<ref>{{cite journal|title=Katy Perry Wins Five People's Choice Awards Including Fave Guest Star for 'How I Met Your Mother'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/how-i-met-your-mother-katy-perry-peoples-choice-280890|magazine=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2012-01-11|accessdate=2014-02-25|journal=|archive-date=2015-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627114001/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/how-i-met-your-mother-katy-perry-peoples-choice-280890|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她还在2011年7月29日上映的3D家庭动画真人电影《[[蓝精灵_(电影)|蓝精灵]]》中饰演[[蓝妹妹|蓝妹妹]]一角，这是她首次参演电影。电影在全球获得财务上的成功<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=smurfs.htm|title=The Smurfs (2011)|publisher=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2011-11-06|archive-date=2015-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210051023/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=smurfs.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然而影评人大多给出差评<ref>{{cite web|title=The Smurfs|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_smurfs/|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2014-01-16|archive-date=2015-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031233249/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_smurfs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年12月10日，她主持了《周六夜现场》，[[蘿蘋|蘿蘋]]在那一集中担任音乐嘉宾。派瑞在该集中的表演获得影评人的普遍好评，他们赞赏她在该集的{{le|周六夜现场数字短片|SNL Digital Short|数字短片}}中与[[安迪·萨姆伯格|安迪·萨姆伯格]]的表演<ref>{{cite journal|last=Rutherford|first=Keith|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/viral-videos/464781/katy-perry-hosts-snl-the-hits-misses-including-a-florence-welch|title=Katy Perry Hosts 'SNL': The Hits & Misses, Including a Florence Welch Spoof|magazine=Billboard|date=2011-12-11|accessdate=2013-08-08|journal=|archive-date=2013-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130821024331/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/viral-videos/464781/katy-perry-hosts-snl-the-hits-misses-including-a-florence-welch|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年3月，她在《[[家有喜旺|家有喜旺]]》名为《女性白人单身模范》（{{lang|en|''Single White Female Role Model''}}）饰演监狱保安里琪（{{lang|en|Rikki}}）<ref>{{cite web|first=Lauren|last=Moraski|title=Katy Perry to portray a prison attendant on 'Raising Hope'|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/katy-perry-to-portray-a-prison-attendant-on-raising-hope/|publisher=CBS News|date=2012-02-22|accessdate=2014-02-25|archive-date=2015-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150712163805/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/katy-perry-to-portray-a-prison-attendant-on-raising-hope/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年7月5日，派瑞的自传纪录片《[[凯蒂佩芮：做自己|凯蒂佩芮：做自己]]》由[[派拉蒙影业|派拉蒙影业]]在各大院线发行<ref>{{cite journal|title=Katy Perry: Part Of Me|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2012/08/14/katy-perry-part-me|magazine=Entertainment Weekly|first=Owen|last=Gleiberman|date=2012-08-14|accessdate=2015-09-13|journal=|archive-date=2015-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150826014715/http://www.ew.com/article/2012/08/14/katy-perry-part-me|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=PrismaticFilm>{{cite journal|last1=Zemler|first1=Emily|title=Katy Perry Premieres Concert TV Special, Explains Why Pop Stars Should Always Play Their Hits|magazine=Billboard|date=2015-03-27|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6516742/katy-perry-epix-prismatic-tour-special|accessdate=2015-07-09|journal=|archive-date=2015-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711004722/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6516742/katy-perry-epix-prismatic-tour-special|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影获得积极评价<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/katy_perry_part_of_me/|title=Katy Perry: Part of Me (2012)|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2012-08-04|archive-date=2015-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151104093911/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/katy_perry_part_of_me/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在全球获得3273万美元[[票房|票房]]<ref name="mojo">{{cite web|title=Katy Perry: Part of Me|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=katyperry.htm|publisher=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2012-08-16|archive-date=2015-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629045724/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=katyperry.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

派瑞于2010年11月发布她的首款香水{{le|Purr|Purr by Katy Perry|Purr}}，正式进军商界。2011年12月，她又发布了第二款香水{{le|Meow!|Meow!}}。两款香水由[[诺德斯特龙百货公司|诺德斯特龙百货公司]]代理销售<ref>{{cite news|last=Howard|first=Hilary|title=Beauty Spots|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/18/fashion/18SPOTS.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2010-11-17|accessdate=2014-08-22|archive-date=2014-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908070622/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/18/fashion/18SPOTS.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Moraski|first=Lauren|title=Katy Perry to perform at Grammy Awards|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/katy-perry-to-perform-at-grammy-awards/|accessdate=2014-08-22|publisher=CBS News|date=2012-02-01|archive-date=2014-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826161045/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/katy-perry-to-perform-at-grammy-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[美国艺电|美国艺电]]招募她宣传他们的新[[资料片|资料片]]《[[模拟人生3：作秀时刻|模拟人生3：作秀时刻]]》<ref>{{cite news|first=Mark|last=Sweeney|title=Katy Perry becomes a Sim|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2012/jan/17/katy-perry-sim-electronic-arts|newspaper=The Guardian|accessdate=2012-01-22|date=2012-02-17|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714135632/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2012/jan/17/katy-perry-sim-electronic-arts|dead-url=no}}</ref>，之后又于2012年6月发布了含有派瑞主题的家具、服饰和发型的物品包《[[模擬市民3組合#凱蒂佩苪甜心包|模拟人生3：凯蒂·派瑞甜心包]]》<ref>{{cite web|title=The Sims 3 Katy Perry's Sweet Treats|url=http://www.ea.com/the-sims-3-kp-sweet-treats|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106040704/http://www.ea.com/the-sims-3-kp-sweet-treats|publisher=Electronic Arts|accessdate=2014-04-03|archivedate=2015-01-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年7月，她成为Popchips的代言人兼形象大使，还投资该公司<ref name="Popchips2012">{{cite news|last=Donnelly|first=Matt|title=First Look: Katy Perry joins Popchips as its face, an investor|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2012/jul/25/entertainment/la-et-mg-katy-perry-pop-chips-endorsement|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2012-07-25|date=2012-07-25|archive-date=2012-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120828232030/http://articles.latimes.com/2012/jul/25/entertainment/la-et-mg-katy-perry-pop-chips-endorsement|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[公告牌|公告牌]]》封她为2012年“年度女性”<ref name=WomanOfTheYear>{{cite journal|title=Katy Perry: Billboard's Woman of the Year|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474944/katy-perry-is-billboards-woman-of-the-year|work=Billboard|date=2012-09-25|accessdate=2014-04-29|journal=|archive-date=2014-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324215149/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474944/katy-perry-is-billboards-woman-of-the-year|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年10月23日，她与罗素·布兰德在拉贾斯坦邦的{{le|伦塔波尔国家公园|Ranthambore National Park}}的一个传统[[印度教|印度教]]婚礼仪式上喜结连理<ref name=Married>{{cite news|first=Prithwish|last=Ganguly|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hollywood/news-interviews/Katy-affirms-Brand-loyalty/articleshow/6808817.cms|title=Katy affirms Brand loyalty|newspaper=The Times of India|date=2010-10-26|accessdate=2010-11-09|archive-date=2010-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101028185902/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hollywood/news-interviews/Katy-affirms-Brand-loyalty/articleshow/6808817.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年12月30日，布兰德宣布两人已离婚，长达14个月的婚姻生活正式结束<ref>{{cite news|last1=Freydkin|first1=Donna|title=Russell Brand, Katy Perry call it quits|url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/story/2011-12-30/katy-perry-russell-brand-divorce/52292040/1|accessdate=2014-08-07|newspaper=USA Today|date=2011-12-30|archive-date=2014-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808123135/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/story/2011-12-30/katy-perry-russell-brand-divorce/52292040/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派瑞后来表示两人职业生涯时间表有冲突，在她就做好了离婚的打算前他渴望孩子{{sfn|Perry|2012|loc=01:11:49|ref=movie}}，而且他把与她离婚的短信发出去后，他再也没有跟她交谈过<ref name="Divorce">{{cite news|last=Saad|first=Nardine|title=Katy Perry's First Vogue Cover|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2013/jun/18/entertainment/la-et-mg-katy-perry-vogue-russell-brand-divorce-text-message-john-mayer-20130618|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=2013-06-18|accessdate=2014-07-23|archive-date=2014-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629055620/http://articles.latimes.com/2013/jun/18/entertainment/la-et-mg-katy-perry-vogue-russell-brand-divorce-text-message-john-mayer-20130618|dead-url=no}}</ref>，况且布兰德之所以跟她离婚，是因为她在商业上的成功和不愿维权的态度<ref name=BrandDocumentary>{{cite news|url=http://smh.com.au/lifestyle/celebrity/documentary-reveals-russell-brand-and-katy-perry-split-caused-by-singers-rising-fame-20150316-1lzwqb.html|title=Documentary reveals Russell Brand and Katy Perry split caused by singer's rising fame|author=Mary Ward|newspaper=The Sydney Morning Herald|date=2015-03-16|accessdate=2015-03-16|archive-date=2015-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150317030804/http://www.smh.com.au/lifestyle/celebrity/documentary-reveals-russell-brand-and-katy-perry-split-caused-by-singers-rising-fame-20150316-1lzwqb.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她最初曾被离婚搞得心烦意乱，一度想轻生<ref name=BillboardCoverStory>{{cite journal|last=Diehl|first=Matt|title=Katy Perry's 'PRISM': The Billboard Cover Story|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5740580/katy-perrys-prism-the-billboard-cover-story|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2013-09-27|date=2013-09-27|journal=|archive-date=2013-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927154909/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5740580/katy-perrys-prism-the-billboard-cover-story|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Heller|first1=Jill|title=Katy Perry Contemplated Suicide After Divorcing Russell Brand, Says Split Was A 'Dark Time'|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/katy-perry-contemplated-suicide-after-divorcing-russell-brand-says-split-was-dark-time-1412872|accessdate=2014-08-07|work=International Business Times|date=2013-09-30|archive-date=2014-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812193250/http://www.ibtimes.com/katy-perry-contemplated-suicide-after-divorcing-russell-brand-says-split-was-dark-time-1412872|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年婚姻结束后<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/Music/2013/06/18/Katy-Perry-says-Russell-Brand-texted-his-desire-to-divorce/UPI-77991371606216/|agency=United Press International|accessdate=2014-08-21|date=2013-06-18|title=Katy Perry says Russell Brand texted his desire to divorce|archive-date=2014-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826113651/http://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/Music/2013/06/18/Katy-Perry-says-Russell-Brand-texted-his-desire-to-divorce/UPI-77991371606216/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，派瑞在当年8月与[[