ite news |last=Wickman |first=Kase |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1713031/katy-perry-roar-vma-finale/ |publisher=MTV News |title=Katy Perry Makes Brooklyn 'Roar' With Epic VMA Finale |date=2013-08-26 |accessdate=2014-05-19 |archive-date=2014-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140520024843/http://www.mtv.com/news/1713031/katy-perry-roar-vma-finale/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Roar#1">{{cite journal|last=Trust|first=Gary|title=Katy Perry Dethrones Robin Thicke Atop Hot 100|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5680131/katy-perry-dethrones-robin-thicke-atop-hot-100|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2013-09-04|date=2013-09-04|journal=|archive-date=2015-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119014159/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5680131/katy-perry-dethrones-robin-thicke-atop-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[無條件愛你|無條件愛你]]》作为第二首单曲于2013年10月16日<ref name="UnconditionallyRelease">{{cite web|last=Benjamin|first=Jeff|title=Katy Perry Wails on New Single "Unconditionally"|url=http://www.fuse.tv/2013/10/katy-perry-unconditionally|publisher=Fuse|accessdate=2013-10-16|date=2013-10-16|archive-date=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721193758/http://www.fuse.tv/2013/10/katy-perry-unconditionally|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在美国的最高排位为第14位<ref>{{cite journal|last=Trust|first=Gary|title=Ask Billboard: Katy Perry Regains No. 1 Momentum|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/5908434/ask-billboard-katy-perry-regains-no-1-momentum|accessdate=2014-09-27|magazine=Billboard|date=2014-02-17|journal=|archive-date=2014-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302044843/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/5908434/ask-billboard-katy-perry-regains-no-1-momentum|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

