st|first=Gary|title=Katy Perry's 'Dark Horse' Gallops to No. 1 on Hot 100|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5885830/katy-perry-dark-horse-hot-100-no-1|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2014-01-29|date=2014-01-29|journal=|archive-date=2015-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150607143222/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5885830/katy-perry-dark-horse-hot-100-no-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年，《[[生日快乐_(歌曲)|生日快乐]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gfa.radioandrecords.com/publishGFA/GFANextPage.asp?sDate=04/21/2014&Format=1 |title=CHR/Top 40 |publisher=Radio & Records |accessdate=2014-04-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140411120609/http://gfa.radioandrecords.com/publishGFA/GFANextPage.asp?sDate=04%2F21%2F2014&Format=1 |archivedate=2014-04-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>和《[[人生就是这样_(歌曲)|人生就是这样]]》<ref>{{cite journal|last=Strecker|first=Erin|title=Katy Perry Releases Lyric Video For New Single 'This Is How We Do'|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/6185609/katy-perry-this-is-how-we-do-lyric-video|accessdate=2014-07-24|magazine=Billboard|date=2014-07-24|journal=|archive-date=2014-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140727081430/http://www.billboard.com/articles/6185609/katy-perry-this-is-how-we-do-lyric-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>接着作为专辑第四首和第五首单曲发布，在百强榜跻身25强<ref name=Hot100History/>。2014年1月11日，派瑞在北京[[国家体育馆|国家体育馆]]参加由[[英菲尼迪|英菲尼迪]]赞助的演唱会，这是她首次到中国演出<ref>{{cite news|title=水果姐凯蒂·派瑞终于来了英菲尼迪万人盛典 林志颖《挚爱》MV全球首发|url=http://epaper.jinghua.cn/html/2014-01/15/content_56745.htm|accessdate=2016-01-31|agency=京华时报|date=2014-01-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131224353/http://epaper.jinghua.cn/html/2014-01/15/content_56745.htm|archivedate=2016-01-31}}</ref>。同年2月与梅尔断交前<ref>{{cite journal|last=Lipshutz|first=Jason|title=Katy Perry & John Mayer Break Up: Report|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5915797/katy-perry-john-mayer-break-up-report|magazine=Billboard|date=2014-02-26|accessdate=2014-02-27|journal=|archive-date=2014-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302094208/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5915797/katy-perry-john-mayer-break-up-report|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=E!|accessdate=2014-03-31|url=http://eonline.com/news/526530/katy-perry-after-john-mayer-new-hair-new-tour-new-very-expensive-hobby|date=2014-03-31|title=Katy Perry After John Mayer: New Hair, New Tour, New Very Expensive Hobby|first=Marc|last=Malkin|archive-date=2015-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150912232234/http://www.eonline.com/news/526530/katy-perry-after-john-mayer-new-hair-new-tour-new-very-expensive-hobby|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，她和他为他的专辑《[[天堂之谷|天堂之谷]]》录制并共同创作了二重唱歌曲《[[你爱的是谁|你爱的是谁]]》。歌曲于2013年8月12日发布<ref>与约翰·梅尔创作《你爱的是谁》：
