*{{cite web|last=Gicas|first=Peter|title=Katy Perry and John Mayer: Inside Their Relationship's Ups and Downs|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/514908/katy-perry-and-john-mayer-inside-their-relationship-ups-and-downs|publisher=E!|accessdate=2014-08-25|date=2014-02-26|archive-date=2014-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140912053154/http://www.eonline.com/news/514908/katy-perry-and-john-mayer-inside-their-relationship-ups-and-downs|dead-url=no}}
*{{cite web|url=https://au.news.yahoo.com/thewest/entertainment/a/20133452/lovers-mayer-and-perry-release-duet-artwork/|publisher=Yahoo! News|title=Lovers Mayer and Perry release duet artwork|date=2013-12-03|accessdate=2015-06-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610224737/https://au.news.yahoo.com/thewest/entertainment/a/20133452/lovers-mayer-and-perry-release-duet-artwork/|archivedate=2015-06-10}}</ref>。派瑞的第三个领衔巡演[[超炫光世界巡回演唱会|超炫光世界巡回演唱会]]于2014年5月启动<ref name=TourBegin/>，2015年10月收官<ref name=ByePrism/>；其中她于4月在广州和上海举办3场演唱会，这是她个首次在中国大陆举办个人演唱会<ref>{{cite news|title=Katy Perry亚洲首演撼动广州 成就歌迷7年心愿|url=http://music.yule.sohu.com/20150419/n411504585.shtml|accessdate=2016-01-31|agency=搜狐|date=2015-04-19|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220172724/http://music.yule.sohu.com/20150419/n411504585.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后的台北站演唱会中，派瑞顺手将一名歌迷挥舞的[[中华民国国旗|中华民国国旗]]披在身上，当时她碰巧穿着一条点缀着[[向日葵|向日葵]]的长裙，引发现场歌迷的热烈反响<ref>{{cite web|title=“水果姐”Katy Perry台北开个唱 披中华民国国旗配太阳花长裙|url=http://www.guancha.cn/local/2015_04_30_317873.shtml|website=观察者网|accessdate=2016-01-31|date=2015-04-30|archive-date=2016-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160209104057/http://www.guancha.cn/local/2015_04_30_317873.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。现场照片流传到社交网站后，在中国大陆网站引发讨论热潮，当地网民表达了对此举的强烈不满，但派瑞及其经纪公司尚未正面回应此事<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1301138 |title=凱蒂佩芮持國旗登台化身太陽花女神 |publisher=《自由時報》 |accessdate=2015-04-28 |archive-date=2015-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150429073223/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1301138 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年9月27日，她献唱2015年里约摇滚节<ref>{{cite news|last1=Leopold|first1=Todd|title=Katy Perry kissed by a girl -- too much|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/09/30/entertainment/katy-perry-kissed-hugged-brazil-feat/|accessdate=2015-10-25|publisher=CNN|date=2015-09-30|archive-date=2015-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151027104220/http://www.cnn.com/2015/09/30/entertainment/katy-perry-kissed-hugged-brazil-feat|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

