[[国际唱片业协会|国际唱片业协会]]将她列入2013年全球顶级发片艺人榜单的第五位<ref name=IFPI>{{cite journal|last=Brandle|first=Lars|title=One Direction Named Most Popular Recording Artist for 2013|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5892841/one-direction-named-most-popular-recording-artist-for-2013|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2014-02-05|date=2014-01-30|journal=|archive-date=2014-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209035811/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5892841/one-direction-named-most-popular-recording-artist-for-2013|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年6月26日，凭借在美国的7200万首数字单曲的认证销量，她被[[美国唱片工业协会|美国唱片工业协会]]宣布为顶级认证数字艺人（{{lang|en|Top Certified Digital Artist}}）<ref name=TopCertified/><ref>{{cite journal|title=Katy Perry Becomes the RIAA's All-Time Top Digital Artist|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/6140789/katy-perry-riaa-top-digital-artist-award-platinum-gold-prism-sales|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2014-06-26|date=2014-06-26|journal=|archive-date=2014-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140628102058/http://www.billboard.com/articles/6140789/katy-perry-riaa-top-digital-artist-award-platinum-gold-prism-sales|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年5月，画家马克·雷登（{{lang|en|Mark Ryden}}）创作的派瑞肖像亮相他在洛杉矶科恩画廊（{{lang|en|Kohn Gallery}}）举办的“90年代同性恋”（{{lang|en|The Gay 90s}}）主题展。跟其他艺人一道，她为展览附带的限量版概念专辑录制了歌曲《{{le|黛西·贝尔 (二人自行车)|Daisy Bell}}》的翻唱版<ref name=MarkRyder>{{cite journal|last=Williams|first=Maxwell|title=Katy Perry Featured on Pop Artist Mark Ryden's $100 'Gay Nineties' Album|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/katy-perry-featured-pop-artist-700730|magazine=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2014-05-03|date=2014-05-02|journal=|archive-date=2014-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506214419/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/katy-perry-featured-pop-artist-700730|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同月，威尔·卡彤（{{lang|en|Will Cotton}}）创作的派瑞肖像出现在[[美国国家肖像画廊|美国国家肖像画廊]]<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6092288/katy-perry-added-to-us-national-portrait-gallery|title=Katy Perry Added to US National Portrait Gallery|date=2014-05-21|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2014-05-29|journal=|archive-date=2014-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140525020318/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6092288/katy-perry-added-to-us-national-portrait-gallery|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年11月23日，派瑞出席[[H&M|H&M]]假期广告促销活动，其中她创作并录制歌曲《[[每一天都值得欢庆|每一天都值得欢庆]]》<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mallenbaum|first1=Carly|title=Katy Perry debuts new 'Holiday' song in H&M commercial|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2015/11/23/katy-perry-debuts-new-holiday-song-hm-commercial/76268216/|accessdate=2015-11-23|work=USA Today|date=2015-11-23|archive-date=2015-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124141459/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2015/11/23/katy-perry-debuts-new-holiday-song-hm-commercial/76268216/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=WORLD PREMIERE: H&M HOLIDAY FEATURING KATY PERRY |url=http://www.hm.com/us/life/culture/h-m-inside/2015/11/happy-and-merry-katy-perry |publisher=H&M |date=2015-11-09 |accessdate=2015-11-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124100512/http://www.hm.com/us/life/culture/h-m-inside/2015/11/happy-and-merry-katy-perry |archivedate=2015-11-24 }}</ref>。

2014年6月17日，派瑞宣布在国会唱片名下建立她自己的唱片公司，名叫[[变形唱片|变形唱片]]。[[费拉斯|费拉斯]]是第一个签约该公司的艺人，派瑞为他的{{le|费拉斯 (迷你专辑)|Ferras (EP)|同名迷你专辑}}出任执行制作人。她为专辑与他录制二重唱歌曲《传奇不朽》（{{lang|en|Legends Never Die}}）<ref>{{cite news|last=Lindner|first=Emilee|title=Katy Perry Starts Her Own Record Label and Reveals First Signee|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1848357/katy-perry-ferras-metamorphosis-music/|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2014-06-17|date=2014-06-17|archive-date=2015-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122082338/http://www.mtv.com/news/1848357/katy-perry-ferras-metamorphosis-music/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她凭借着3900万美元的收入入选《福布斯》2013年“全球音乐界最赚钱女性”榜单<ref name="#2">{{cite journal|last=Greenburg|first=Zack O'Malley|title=The Top-Earning Women In Music 2013|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/zackomalleygreenburg/2013/12/11/the-top-earning-women-in-music-2013/|magazine=Forbes|accessdate=2013-12-11|date=2013-12-11|journal=|archive-date=2013-12-15|archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20131215130617/http://www.forbes.com/sites/zackomalleygreenburg/2013/12/11/the-top-earning-women-in-music-2013/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，后来又凭借4000万美元收入在他们2014年的榜单中名列第五<ref name="#3">{{cite journal|last=Greenburg|first=Zack O'Malley|title=The Top-Earning Women In Music 2014|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/zackomalleygreenburg/2014/11/04/the-top-earning-women-in-music-2014/|magazine=Forbes|accessdate=2014-11-27|date=2014-11-04|journal=|archive-date=2014-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141127085735/http://www.forbes.com/sites/zackomalleygreenburg/2014/11/04/the-top-earning-women-in-music-2014/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年，凭借1.35亿的收入，《福布斯》再次将派瑞列入榜单头位，封其为“全球收入最高的女艺人”，宣称她是2015年收入最高的女性名人，把她放进杂志百强名人榜的第三位<ref>2015年《福布斯》排行：
