*{{cite journal|last=Greenburg|first=Zack O'Malley|title=The World's Highest-Paid Women In Music 2015|journal=Forbes|date=2015-11-04|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/zackomalleygreenburg/2015/11/04/the-worlds-highest-paid-women-in-music-2015/|accessdate=2015-11-05|archive-date=2015-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151104161118/http://www.forbes.com/sites/zackomalleygreenburg/2015/11/04/the-worlds-highest-paid-women-in-music-2015/|dead-url=no}}
*{{cite journal|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/zackomalleygreenburg/2015/12/08/the-worlds-highest-paid-musicians-of-2015/|journal=Forbes|date=2015-12-08|accessdate=2015-12-24|first=Zack O'Malley|last=Greenburg|title=The World's Highest-Paid Musicians Of 2015|archive-date=2015-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225111722/http://www.forbes.com/sites/zackomalleygreenburg/2015/12/08/the-worlds-highest-paid-musicians-of-2015/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

