2016年5月，佩里确认她正创作新的音乐<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2016/05/04/katy-perry-body-positivity/|publisher=Mashable|date=2016-05-04|accessdate=2016-05-08|title=Katy Perry on loving her body: 'I'm curvy, I'm not sample-size'|first=David|last=Yi|archive-date=2016-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507213148/http://mashable.com/2016/05/04/katy-perry-body-positivity/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她为[[NBC体育|NBC体育]]所转播的[[2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会]]创作主题曲《[[崛起_(歌曲)|崛起]]》，该曲于2016年7月14日释出。佩里之所以选择单独发行该曲，而不把它收入专辑，“是因为现在比以往更重要是，我们的世界必须团结起来。”NBC也认为这首歌的励志主题“直接传播了奥林匹克及其运动员精神的信息”<ref>{{cite news|title=NBC OLYMPICS FEATURES NEW KATY PERRY ANTHEM "RISE"|url=http://nbcsportsgrouppressbox.com/2016/07/14/nbc-olympics-features-new-katy-perry-anthem-rise/|accessdate=2016-07-14|publisher=NBC Sports|date=2016-07-14|archive-date=2016-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160718034040/http://nbcsportsgrouppressbox.com/2016/07/14/nbc-olympics-features-new-katy-perry-anthem-rise/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。该曲在澳大利亞單曲榜以第一名亮相<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.noise11.com/news/australian-singles-katy-perry-rise-has-a-go-at-no-1-20160725|title=Australian Singles: Katy Perry 'Rise' Has A Go At No 1|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|date=2016-07-25|accessdate=2016-07-25|publisher=Noise11.com|archive-date=2016-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160725141449/http://www.noise11.com/news/australian-singles-katy-perry-rise-has-a-go-at-no-1-20160725|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在美国則名列第11<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7446774/katy-perry-rise-britney-spears-make-me-debut-hot-100|title=Katy Perry's 'Rise' & Britney Spears' 'Make Me' Debut in Hot 100's Top 20|last=Trust|first=Gary|journal=Billboard|date=2016-07-25|accessdate=2016-07-25|archive-date=2016-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160726140448/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7446774/katy-perry-rise-britney-spears-make-me-debut-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年8月，佩里称她渴望去加入一些可以「聯繫起来而且鼓舞人心的」素材<ref>{{cite web|url=http://amp.cbslocal.com/2016/08/18/katy-perry-new-music-taking-chances/|title=Katy Perry Is 'Taking Chances' & 'Not Rushing' Her New Music|date=2016-08-18|accessdate=2016-08-19|first=Sarah|last=Carroll|publisher=97.1 AMP Radio|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819125902/http://amp.cbslocal.com/2016/08/18/katy-perry-new-music-taking-chances/|archivedate=2016-08-19}}</ref>并告诉[[瑞安·西克雷斯特|瑞安·西克雷斯特]]她「不着急」制作第五张专辑，并补充说：「尝试不同的制作人，不同的合作者，还有不同的风格让我感觉很有意思。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://onairwithryan.iheart.com/onair/ryan-seacrest-52241/katy-perry-reveals-shes-experimenting-with-15019828/|work=On Air with Ryan Seacrest|title=Katy Perry Reveals She's 'Experimenting' With New Album, Talks Forthcoming Shoe Collection|date=2016-08-18|accessdate=2016-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920140320/http://onairwithryan.iheart.com/onair/ryan-seacrest-52241/katy-perry-reveals-shes-experimenting-with-15019828/|archive-date=2016-09-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2017年2月10日，佩里發行了新單曲《[[鍊上節奏|鍊上節奏]]》<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7685135/katy-perry-chained-to-the-rhtyhm-disco-balls-new-single|title=Katy Perry Leaves Chained Disco Balls Playing New Single In Various Cities|date=2017-02-08|accessdate=2017-02-08|first=Lyndsey|last=Havens|magazine=Billboard|journal=|archive-date=2017-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170209013629/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7685135/katy-perry-chained-to-the-rhtyhm-disco-balls-new-single|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲在匈牙利夺冠<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://zene.slagerlistak.hu/radios-top-40-jatszasi-lista/2017/15|title=Archívum – Slágerlisták – MAHASZ|date=2017-04-07|accessdate=2017-04-27|publisher=[[Association_of_Hungarian_Record_Companies|Rádiós Top 40 játszási lista]]|archive-date=2017-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170426151417/http://zene.slagerlistak.hu/radios-top-40-jatszasi-lista/2017/15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，在美国取得了第4名<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7694385/hot-100-ed-sheeran-katy-perry-bruno-mars|first=Gary|last=Trust|title=Ed Sheeran Tops Hot 100, Katy Perry Debuts at No. 4 & Bruno Mars, Rihanna & The Weeknd All Hit Top 10|magazine=Billboard|date=2017-02-21|accessdate=2017-02-21|journal=|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612170751/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7694385/hot-100-ed-sheeran-katy-perry-bruno-mars|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随着歌曲的发行，Spotify宣布会在2017年夏季第五张录音室专辑发行前展开一轮宣传活动<ref>{{cite news|last1=Shaw|first1=Lucas|title=Spotify Befriends Katy Perry in Quest to Win Artists' Favor|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-02-10/spotify-befriends-katy-perry-in-quest-to-win-artists-favor?curator=MediaREDEF|accessdate=2017-03-01|publisher=[[彭博新聞社|Bloomberg News]]|date=2017-02-10|archive-date=2017-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301183330/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-02-10/spotify-befriends-katy-perry-in-quest-to-win-artists-favor?curator=MediaREDEF|dead-url=no}}</ref>。专辑的第二张单曲《[[秀色可餐|秀色可餐]]》由[[Migos|Migos]]参与客串，于4月28日发行<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Tom|first1=Lauren|title=Katy Perry Unveils 'Bon Appetit' Single Art, Release Date & Migos Feature|magazine=Billboard|date=2017-04-26|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7775316/katy-perry-bon-appetit-single-art-release-date-migos|accessdate=2017-04-27|journal=|archive-date=2017-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170427050858/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7775316/katy-perry-bon-appetit-single-art-release-date-migos|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

