-witness-world-wide-49-million-views |archivedate=2017-06-15 }}</ref>專輯的宣傳巡演[[見證巡迴演唱會|見證巡迴演唱會]]於2017年9月開啟，計畫於2018年8月結束。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/3031006/katy-perry-witness-tour-delays-openers/ |title=Katy Perry Has Good News And Bad News About Her Witness Tour |first=Madeline |last=Roth |date=2017-08-17 |accessdate=2017-08-18 |publisher=MTV News |archive-date=2017-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170817231246/http://www.mtv.com/news/3031006/katy-perry-witness-tour-delays-openers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年6月15日，[[凱文·哈里斯|凱文·哈里斯]]專輯《[[音浪強襲_第1輯|音浪強襲 第1輯]]》歌曲《[[戀愛感覺|戀愛感覺]]》發行，佩芮參與了歌曲客串。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hotnewhiphop.com/calvin-harris-announces-single-with-big-sean-pharrell-and-katy-perry-news.33773.html?|publisher={{tsl|en|HotNewHipHop||HotNewHipHop}}|date=2017-06-14|accessdate=2017-06-14|title=Calvin Harris Announces Single With Big Sean, Pharrell, & Katy Perry|first=Mitch|last=Findlay|archive-date=2017-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170622155231/http://www.hotnewhiphop.com/calvin-harris-announces-single-with-big-sean-pharrell-and-katy-perry-news.33773.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>歌曲在英國取得了冠軍，成為佩芮在該國第5張冠軍單曲。<ref>{{cite web|title=Calvin Harris dethrones Despacito to claim his eighth Number 1 single|first=Jack|last=White|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/calvin-harris-dethrones-despacito-to-claim-his-eighth-number-1-single__19932/|publisher=[[官方榜单公司|Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=2017-08-11|date=2017-08-11|archive-date=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811224622/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/calvin-harris-dethrones-despacito-to-claim-his-eighth-number-1-single__19932/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

