在职业生涯的早期阶段，派瑞的音乐风格受福音吸引，而她渴望像[[艾米·格兰特|艾米·格兰特]]那样的成功<ref>{{cite web|title=Katy Perry on the 180 That Saved Her Career|url=http://www.npr.org/2013/10/26/240760441/katy-perry-returns-with-a-roar|publisher=NPR|date=2013-10-26|accessdate=2014-02-03|archive-date=2015-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151104094422/http://www.npr.org/2013/10/26/240760441/katy-perry-returns-with-a-roar|dead-url=no}}</ref>。15岁时，她听了[[皇后乐队|皇后乐队]]的歌曲《[[Killer_Queen|杀手女王]]》，称这首歌启发她追寻音乐生涯<ref>{{cite journal|last=Schneider|first=Marc|title=Katy Perry Wants a 'Fucking Vacation' After Next Single|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/488619/katy-perry-wants-a-f-ing-vacation-after-next-single|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2014-02-03|date=2012-05-12|journal=|archive-date=2014-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713083643/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/488619/katy-perry-wants-a-f-ing-vacation-after-next-single|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她表示称乐队主唱[[弗雷迪·默丘里|弗雷迪·默丘里]]给她的影响最大，表示“他的讽刺性歌曲创作手法和‘我才不在乎’的态度”启发了她的音乐灵感<ref>{{cite journal|title=Freddie Mercury inspired Katy Perry to 'Kiss a Girl'|url=http://www.nme.com/news/queen/40017|magazine=NME|date=2008-09-26|accessdate=2014-02-03|journal=|archive-date=2014-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106041511/http://www.nme.com/news/queen/40017|dead-url=no}}</ref>。为了表示对乐队的敬意，她给她的第三款香水起名为“杀手女王”<ref>{{cite web|title=Killer Qieen Katy Perry for women|url=http://www.fragrantica.com/perfume/Katy-Perry/Killer-Queen-18318.html|publisher=fragrantica}}</ref>。派瑞表示[[海滩男孩|海滩男孩]]和他们的专辑《[[宠物之声|宠物之声]]》对她的音乐有着相当的影响力：“（它）是我最喜欢的唱片，她对我的所有歌曲有着相当大的影响。我曾甄选过所有旋律都是因它而起的<ref>{{cite web|title=Katy Perry, The Things They Say|url=http://www.contactmusic.com/story/the-things-they-say_3902539|publisher=Contactmusic.com|accessdate=2014-02-03|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006114531/http://www.contactmusic.com/story/the-things-they-say_3902539|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”这位歌手还对[[披头士|披头士]]的[[The_Beatles_(专辑)|同名专辑]]怀有崇高的敬意，表示这两张专辑是“唯一一样我听了足足两年的东西”<ref name=InterviewWiig>{{cite journal|last=Wiig|first=Kristen|authorlink=Kristen Wiig|title=Katy Perry|url=http://www.interviewmagazine.com/music/katy-perry#page4|magazine=Interview|accessdate=2014-02-03|date=2012-03-02|journal=|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222061428/http://www.interviewmagazine.com/music/katy-perry#page4|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[艾拉妮丝·莫莉塞特|艾拉妮丝·莫莉塞特]]和她1995年的专辑《{{le|小碎丸|Jagged Little Pill}}》是显著的音乐灵感，促成了后来与莫莉塞特的长期合作伙伴布拉德合作的结果。派瑞表示，“《小碎丸》是史上最完美的女性唱片。那张专辑上有一首献给所有人的歌。上面所有的歌都唱到了我的心坎上。它们是永恒的。”此外，派瑞还借用了{{le|帕蒂·格里芬|Patty Griffin}}的《{{le|花红胜火|Flaming Red}}》和{{le|乔纳瑟·布鲁克|Jonatha Brooke}}的《插上双翼的10美分》（{{lang|en|10 Cent Wings}}）的影响<ref name=BillboardQA>{{cite journal|last=Mitchell|first=Gail|title=Katy Perry Q&A: Billboard's Woman of the Year 2012|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/473939/katy-perry-qa-billboards-woman-of-the-year-2012?page=0%2C1|magazine=Billboard|date=2012-11-30|accessdate=2012-11-30|journal=|archive-date=2013-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508091858/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/473939/katy-perry-qa-billboards-woman-of-the-year-2012?page=0%2C1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派瑞打算把她的大部分当成是[[琼尼·米歇尔|琼尼·米歇尔]]，发行民谣和原音音乐<ref>{{cite news|last=Michaels|first=Sean|title=Katy Perry wants to go folk acoustic – in style of Joni Mitchell|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/oct/01/katy-perry-plans-acoustic-folk-album|newspaper=The Guardian|accessdate=2014-02-03|archive-date=2014-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223005644/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/oct/01/katy-perry-plans-acoustic-folk-album|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派瑞的自传纪录片《[[凯蒂佩芮：做自己|凯蒂佩芮：做自己]]》受到《{{le|麦当娜：真心话大冒险|Madonna: Truth or Dare}}》的大部分影响。她敬佩[[麦当娜|麦当娜]]彻底改变自己的能力，表示“我要逐渐进化成麦当娜<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1682661/katy-perry-part-of-me-movie.jhtml|title=Katy Perry's 'Part of Me' Film Inspired By Madonna|first=James|last=Dinh|publisher=MTV News|date=2012-04-06|accessdate=2014-04-29|archive-date=2013-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109132227/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1682661/katy-perry-part-of-me-movie.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

派瑞列举出多位给予她创作灵感的艺术家。她认为[[格温·史蒂芬妮|格温·史蒂芬妮]]和[[碧玉_(歌手)|碧玉]]给了她影响，尤其钦佩碧玉“乐于永远抓住机会”<ref name=BillboardQA />。《[[烟火_(歌曲)|烟火]]》的灵感出自[[杰克·凯鲁亚克|杰克·凯鲁亚克]]书作《[[在路上|在路上]]》的一篇文章，文中作者比较了把自己的毕生活得像穿越天际的烟火一样绚烂和怀着敬畏之心观赏烟火的两类人<ref>{{harvnb|Friedlander|2012|p=123}}</ref>。她的第二个巡回演唱会加州梦之旅，让人想起《[[爱丽丝梦游仙境|爱丽丝梦游仙境]]》和《[[绿野仙踪|绿野仙踪]]》<ref>{{cite journal|title=Katy Perry's 'California Dreams' Tour: What the Critics Are Saying|magazine=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2011-06-19|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/katy-perrys-california-dreams-tour-203209|accessdate=2014-08-06|journal=|archive-date=2014-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908070039/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/katy-perrys-california-dreams-tour-203209|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她也把她的歌曲《[[黑马_(歌曲)|黑马]]》背后的影响归功于1996年电影《{{le|魔女游戏 (电影)|The Craft (film)|魔女游戏}}》<ref>{{cite journal|last=Rutherford|first=Kevin|title=Katy Perry Reveals 'Prism' Influences, Adds Stripped-Down Performances at Album Release Event|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5763220/katy-perry-reveals-prism-influences-adds-stripped-down|magazine=Billboard|date=2013-10-22|accessdate=2013-12-09|journal=|archive-date=2013-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027052306/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5763220/katy-perry-reveals-prism-influences-adds-stripped-down|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而《棱镜》则受[[艾克哈特·托勒|艾克哈特·托勒]]的书作《{{le|当下的力量|The Power of Now}}》影响。<ref>{{cite web|last=Diehl|first=Matt|title=Katy Perry's 'PRISM': The Billboard Cover Story|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5740580/katy-perrys-prism-the-billboard-cover-story|publisher=Billboard|date=2013-09-27|accessdate=2013-10-04|archive-date=2013-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927154909/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5740580/katy-perrys-prism-the-billboard-cover-story|dead-url=no}}</ref>

