派瑞自封为“披着流行歌星外衣的创作型歌手”<ref>{{cite journal|last=Wallace|first=Amy|title=Katy Perry's GQ Profile Outtakes: Going Back to School, Dating Musicians, and Plastic Surgery|url=http://www.gq.com/blogs/the-feed/2014/02/cover-katy-perry-interview-outtakes.html|magazine=GQ|date=2014-01-19|accessdate=2014-02-02|journal=|archive-date=2014-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224060306/http://www.gq.com/blogs/the-feed/2014/02/cover-katy-perry-interview-outtakes.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，认为诚恳的歌曲创作对她很重要。她告诉《[[美丽佳人|美丽佳人]]》：“我感觉将我与我的很多同龄人分隔开的神秘魔法是一种变得脆弱、真实和诚实的勇气<ref name=Marie/>。”[[克里斯汀·韦格|克里斯汀·韦格]]评论道：“派瑞的歌能做得简朴、清新且有感染力，表面潜藏着一片百感交集、目标混乱和自相矛盾的冲击相交织的海洋，足以填补一张[[卡洛尔·金|卡洛尔·金]]的专辑<ref name=InterviewWiig/>。”《[[芝加哥论坛报|芝加哥论坛报]]》的{{le|格雷格·科特|Greg Kot}}表示，“被认真对待可能是派瑞最大的挑战<ref>{{cite news|last=Kot|first=Greg|title=Katy Perry album review; Prism reviewed|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-10-20/entertainment/chi-kate-perry-prism-review-20131020_1_katy-perry-russell-brand-album-review|newspaper=Chicago Tribune|accessdate=2014-02-05|date=2013-10-20|archive-date=2013-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022015412/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-10-20/entertainment/chi-kate-perry-prism-review-20131020_1_katy-perry-russell-brand-album-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》把她标榜为“当代最有天赋的流行巨星——她的热曲听上去像一种实验的暗示<ref>{{cite news|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2013-09-06|accessdate=2014-08-07|title=Fall Pop Music Preview: An Abundance of Rhythms and Styles|url=http://nytimes.com/2013/09/08/arts/music/fall-pop-music-preview-an-abundance-of-rhythms-and-styles.html|first1=Jon|last1=Pareles|first2=Ben|last2=Ratliff|first3=Jon|last3=Carmanica|first4=Nate|last4=Chinen|archive-date=2015-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415231943/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/09/08/arts/music/fall-pop-music-preview-an-abundance-of-rhythms-and-styles.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。”《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的{{le|兰德尔·罗伯茨|Randall Roberts}}称她在她的歌词中使用习语和隐喻，“陈词滥调”层出不穷<ref name=LATimesReview>{{cite news|last=Roberts|first=Randall|title=Review: Hits pack Katy Perry's 'Prism'|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-katy-perry-prism-review-20131022,0,6156766.story|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2014-02-04|date=2013-10-22|archive-date=2013-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022153039/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-katy-perry-prism-review-20131022,0,6156766.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>。纵观整个职业生涯，派瑞合作创作的歌曲被[[魔法少女席琳娜|魔法少女席琳娜]]<ref name=RockGodSelena>{{cite news|last=Vena|first=Jocelyn|title=Selena Gomez 'Had To Fight' To Get Katy Perry Song 'Rock God'|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1648390/selena-gomez-had-fight-get-katy-perry-song-rock-god.jhtml|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2010-09-22|archive-date=2014-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203015006/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1648390/selena-gomez-had-fight-get-katy-perry-song-rock-god.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=MoreLikeIt>{{cite AV media notes|title=When the Sun Goes Down|others=Selena Gomez & the Scene|year=2011|publisher=Hollywood Records}}</ref>、[[杰西·詹姆斯|杰西·詹姆斯]]<ref>{{cite AV media notes|title=Jessie James|others=Jessie James|year=2009|publisher=Mercury Records/The Island Def Jam Music Group}}</ref>、[[凯莉·克莱森|凯莉·克莱森]]<ref name=AllKellyWanted>{{cite AV media notes|title=All I Ever Wanted|others=Kelly Clarkson|year=2009|publisher=RCA Records/19 Recordings}}</ref>、{{le|莱斯利·罗伊|Lesley Roy}}<ref name="KatyLesley">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/second-cup-cafe-lesley-roy/|title=Second Cup Cafe: Lesley Roy|last=Castellanos|first=Melissa|publisher=CBS News|date=2008-09-26|accessdate=2014-05-24|archive-date=2014-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140908070609/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/second-cup-cafe-lesley-roy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[布兰妮·斯皮尔斯|布兰妮·斯皮尔斯]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1718479/britney-spears-katy-perry-britney-jean-passenger/|publisher=MTV News|title=Bri