=== 聲樂 ===
派瑞拥有从Eb3到C#7三个八度的轻抒情女高音音域<ref>{{cite web|title=Vocal Profile: Katy Perry|url=http://thevocalpoint.tumblr.com/post/159126910490/vocal-profile-katy-perry|access-date=2017-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171026060153/http://thevocalpoint.tumblr.com/post/159126910490/vocal-profile-katy-perry|archive-date=2017-10-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。对她声线的评价褒贬不一，《[[卫报|卫报]]》的贝蒂·克拉克（{{lang|en|Betty Clarke}}）评论称她的声音“锋芒毕露得强有力”<ref>{{cite news|last=Clarke|first=Betty|title=Katy Perry – review|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/oct/01/katy-perry-itunes-festival-review|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2013-10-01|accessdate=2014-02-05|archive-date=2014-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223005639/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/oct/01/katy-perry-itunes-festival-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》的罗布·谢菲尔德（{{lang|en|Rob Sheffield}}）称派瑞在《花漾年华》中声音“被加工成[[断奏|断奏]]的响音”<ref name=SheffieldDream/>。{{le|musicOMH|musicOMH}}的达伦·哈维（{{lang|en|Darren Harvey}}）将派瑞在《花漾派对》中声音与[[艾拉妮丝·莫莉塞特|艾拉妮丝·莫莉塞特]]的声线作比较，称都具备一把“转八度中音节的活泼嗓音”<ref>{{cite web|last=Harvey|first=Darren|title=Katy Perry – One of the Boys|url=http://www.musicomh.com/reviews/albums/katy-perry-one-of-the-boys|work=musicOMH|date=2008-09-15|accessdate=2014-02-05|archive-date=2015-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151104095638/http://www.musicomh.com/reviews/albums/katy-perry-one-of-the-boys|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而《[[新音乐快递|新音乐快递]]》的亚历克斯·米勒（{{lang|en|Alex Miller}}）则感觉在《花漾派对》中“派瑞的问题经常出在她的声线上”，指出“循着旋律的某个地方，有人相信她像一位不错的、勇气十足的摇滚小妞<ref>{{cite journal|last=Miller|first=Alex|title=NME Album Reviews – Katy Perry|url=http://www.nme.com/reviews/9900|magazine=NME|accessdate=2014-02-05|journal=|archive-date=2014-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116104108/http://www.nme.com/reviews/9900|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”相反，《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的贝尔纳黛·麦克纳尔蒂（{{lang|en|Bernadette McNulty}}）一篇关于《棱镜》专辑推广演唱会的评论称赞她的“摇滚小妞声音<ref>{{cite news|last=McNulty|first=Bernadette|title=Katy Perry, iTunes Festival, Roundhouse, review|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/live-music-reviews/10347052/Katy-Perry-iTunes-Festival-Roundhouse-review.html|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2014-02-05|date=2013-10-01|archive-date=2014-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322153914/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/live-music-reviews/10347052/Katy-Perry-iTunes-Festival-Roundhouse-review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。

