ref>。

派瑞的时装往往采用幽默、明亮的色彩和与食物有关的主题<ref>{{cite news|last=Larson|first=John|title=Katy Perry // "Teenage Dream"|url=http://www.tacomaweekly.com/citylife/view/katy_perry/|newspaper=Tacoma Weekly|accessdate=2013-06-19|date=2010-09-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109082707/http://www.tacomaweekly.com/citylife/view/katy_perry/|archivedate=2013-11-09}}</ref>，例如她的标志性薄荷旋风连衣裙<ref name="pb5">{{cite journal|last=Menyes|first=Carolyn|title=Katy Perry Asked to Ditch Hazardous Peppermint Bra|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/481674/katy-perry-asked-to-ditch-hazardous-peppermint-bra|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2013-06-19|date=2012-07-12|journal=|archive-date=2013-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130529054945/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/481674/katy-perry-asked-to-ditch-hazardous-peppermint-bra|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[时尚_(杂志)|时尚]]》形容她是“唯一一个永远不羞于在任何领域中蛮横或走极端的人”<ref>{{cite journal|title=Fashion Fireworks: Katy Perry's Best Performance Looks|url=http://www.vogue.com/vogue-daily/article/fashion-fireworks-katy-perrys-best-performance-looks/#1|magazine=Vogue|accessdate=2014-02-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131221061713/http://www.vogue.com/vogue-daily/article/fashion-fireworks-katy-perrys-best-performance-looks/#1|archivedate=2013-12-21|journal=}}</ref>，而《{{le|魅力 (杂志)|Glamour (magazine)|魅力}}》则给她取了“怪癖女王”的绰号<ref>{{cite journal|last=Lyons Powell|first=Hannah|title=Katy Perry's Changing Style and Fashion|url=http://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/fashion/celebrity-fashion/2010/08/katy-perry-craziest-fashion-and-style-ever#!image-number=23|magazine=Glamour|accessdate=2014-02-06|journal=|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219033238/http://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/fashion/celebrity-fashion/2010/08/katy-perry-craziest-fashion-and-style-ever#!image-number=23|archive-date=2014-02-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2009年2月，派瑞告诉《[[17_(美國雜誌)|17]]》，她的时装风格是“有点像不同东西的堆砌品”，声称她享受她的服装带来的幽默<ref name="17Style">{{cite journal|url=http://www.seventeen.com/fashion/special/style-blog/katy-perry-fashion-qa-interview|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090908222401/http://www.seventeen.com/fashion/special/style-blog/katy-perry-fashion-qa-interview|title=Find Out What Influences Katy Perry's Cute Style!|date=2009-02-05|magazine=Seventeen|accessdate=2014-04-29|archivedate=2009-09-08|journal=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她还表示自己对时尚有“[[解离性人格疾患|多重人格障碍]]”<ref name=HarpersBazaar/>。派瑞将[[關·史蒂芬妮|關·史蒂芬妮]]、{{le|雪莉·曼森|Shirley Manson}}、[[科洛·塞维尼|科洛·塞维尼]]、{{le|达芙妮·吉尼斯|Daphne Guinness}}、[[娜塔莉·波特曼|娜塔莉·波特曼]]和虚构人物[[洛丽塔|洛丽塔]]列为她的时尚偶像<ref name=WMag/><ref>{{cite news|last=Young|first=Katy|title=Katy Perry reveals her perfume preferences|url=http://fashion.telegraph.co.uk/beauty/news-features/TMG10347572/Katy-Perry-reveals-her-perfume-preferences.html|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2013-10-01|date=2013-10-01|archive-date=2013-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002154813/http://fashion.telegraph.co.uk/beauty/news-features/TMG10347572/Katy-Perry-reveals-her-perfume-preferences.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在社交媒体上，派瑞于2013年11月超越[[贾斯汀·比伯|贾斯汀·比伯]]成为最多关注者的Twitter用户<ref>{{cite news |first=Sean |last=Hollister |url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/11/3/5061834/katy-perry-passes-justin-bieber-as-most-popular-person-on-twitter |title=Katy Perry passes Justin Bieber as most popular person on Twitter |newspaper=The Verge |date=2013-11-03 |accessdate=2013-11-04 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104135526/http://www.theverge.com/2013/11/3/5061834/katy-perry-passes-justin-bieber-as-most-popular-person-on-twitter |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年1月，她成为首位在该网站上获得5000万个关注者的人士<ref name="Katy Perry Hits 50 Million Twitter Followers">{{cite journal|last=Buli|first=Liv|title=Katy Perry Hits 50 Million Twitter Followers|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5893809/katy-perry-hits-50-million-twitter-followers|date=2014-01-31|accessdate=2014-02-01|magazine=Billboard|journal=|archive-date=2014-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140204085338/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5893809/katy-perry-hits-50-million-twitter-followers|dead-url=no}}</ref>，创下最多Twitter关注者的2015年吉尼斯世界记录<ref name=Guinness2015>{{cite journal|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/wherever-they-may-roam-metallica-set-guinness-world-record-for-touring-20140904|magazine=Rolling Stone|date=2014-09-04|accessdate=2014-09-04|first=Kory|last=Grow|title=Wherever They May Roam: Metallica Set Guinness World Record for Touring|journal=|archive-date=2014-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140905012331/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/wherever-they-may-roam-metallica-set-guinness-world-record-for-touring-20140904|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并于2016年7月该站获得9000万关注者的第一人<ref name=90Twitter>{{cite journal|last=McIntyre|first=Hugh|title=Katy Perry Just Hit 90 Million Twitter Followers. Is 100 Million Coming Soon?|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/hughmcintyre/2016/07/01/katy-perry-is-now-the-first-person-to-hit-90-million-followers-on-twitter/#61b04f901fdf|date=2016-07-01|accessdate=2016-07-02|magazine=Forbes|journal=|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701234752/http://www.forbes.com/sites/hughmcintyre/2016/07/01/katy-perry-is-now-the-first-person-to-hit-90-million-followers-on-twitter/#61b04f901fdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《福布斯》专栏作家多萝西·波梅兰茨（{{lang|en|Dorothy Pomerantz}}）赞扬派瑞将社交媒体运用得得心应手，表示“派瑞是最优秀的Twitter用户，她跟歌迷们对话、分享有趣的照片和视频的方式，使他们都觉得派瑞是他们知心朋友<ref>{{cite journal|title=Katy Perry – In Photos: Social Networking Superstars|url=http://www.forbes.com/pictures/mfl45lfhm/katy-perry-4/|accessdate=2014-02-06|first=Dorothy|last=Pomerantz|magazine=Forbes|journal=|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222030326/http://www.forbes.com/pictures/mfl45lfhm/katy-perry-4/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《公告牌》的基思·考菲尔德（{{lang|en|Keith Caulfield}}）表示，她“是一位似乎有着巨大人气的罕见名人，却真正的跟崇拜她的凯蒂猫（{{lang|en|KatyCats}}）进行零距离互动<ref>{{cite news|last=Gundersen|first=Edna|title=Katy Perry tells how to 'tame the social media dragon'|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2013/10/21/twitter-queen-katy-perry-offers-social-media-tips/3098961/|newspaper=USA Today|accessdate=2014-02-04|date=2013-10-21|archive-date=2014-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140205092732/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2013/10/21/twitter-queen-katy-perry-offers-social-media-tips/3098961/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

