职业生涯期间派瑞支持了众多慈善机构和事业。她向福利的组织作出贡献，并尤其关注儿童的生活。2013年4月，她加入了[[联合国儿童基金会|联合国儿童基金会]]，帮助改善[[马达加斯加|马达加斯加]]儿童的教育和营养<ref>{{cite web|title=Katy Perry teams up with UNICEF and visits children in Madagascar|url=http://www.unicef.org/media/media_68612.html|publisher=UNICEF|accessdate=2013-04-07|archive-date=2015-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151104100227/http://www.unicef.org/media/media_68612.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年12月3日，因“特别注重在机构的工作中使年轻人感到愉快，改善世界上最脆弱的儿童和青少年的生活，她被正式任命为{{le|联合国儿童基金会亲善大使列表|List of UNICEF Goodwill Ambassadors|联合国儿童基金会亲善大使}}，<ref name=UNICEFGoodwillAmbassador>{{cite web|title=Katy Perry is UNICEF's newest Goodwill Ambassador|url=http://www.unicef.org/media/media_71241.html|publisher=UNICEF|date=2013-12-03|accessdate=2014-04-28|archive-date=2015-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151104100230/http://www.unicef.org/media/media_71241.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”她还安排将超炫光世界巡回演唱会门票所产生的资金交给儿童基金会<ref name=PrismaticNorthAmerica>{{cite journal|title=Katy Perry Cues Up 'Prismatic' World Tour|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/katy-perry-cues-up-prismatic-world-tour-20140115|magazine=Rolling Stone|date=2014-01-15|last=Ryan|first=Reed|accessdate=2014-04-28|journal=|archive-date=2016-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507172807/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/katy-perry-cues-up-prismatic-world-tour-20140115|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年9月，她与[[雷文-西蒙尼|雷文-西蒙尼]]、[[沙奎尔·奥尼尔|沙奎尔·奥尼尔]]和《{{le|彻底改变：家庭再造|Extreme Makeover: Home Edition}}》剧组成员为马里兰州巴尔的摩的失足青年建造并设计了Boys Hope/Girls Hope基金会庇护所<ref>{{cite web|title=Boys Hope/Girls Hope|publisher=American Broadcasting Company|url=http://abc.go.com/shows/extreme-makeover-home-edition/episode-guide/episode-801-boys-hope-girls-hope|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018094040/http://abc.go.com/shows/extreme-makeover-home-edition/episode-guide/episode-801-boys-hope-girls-hope|accessdate=2014-04-28|archivedate=2014-10-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。她还支持儿童教育。2014年5月，派瑞和其他被选中的艺人为画家马克·瑞登（{{lang|en|Mark Ryden}}）艺术展的概念专辑《快乐90后》（{{lang|en|''The Gay 90s''}}）的，录制了歌曲《戴茜·贝尔（两人自行车）》（{{lang|en|''Daisy Bell (Bicycle Built for Two)''}}）的翻唱版。出自专辑销售的所有收益将捐给支持贫困小学音乐教育的慈善机构{{le|小子要摇滚|Little Kids Rock}}<ref name=MarkRyder />。2014年6月，她联手[[史泰博公司|史泰博公司]]开展“吼出来”（{{lang|en|Make Roar Happen}}）项目，为支持公立学校教师和教室资源的组织{{le|DonorsChoose|DonorsChoose}}捐了100万<ref>{{cite journal|title=Katy Perry and Staples 'Make Roar Happen' to Help Support Teachers|first=Roy|last=Trakin|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/branding/6121146/katy-perry-and-staples-make-roar-happen-to-help-support-teachers|magazine=Billboard|date=2014-06-12|accessdate=2014-06-18|journal=|archive-date=2014-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140622012143/http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/branding/6121146/katy-perry-and-staples-make-roar-happen-to-help-support-teachers|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

派瑞还支持帮助[[癌症|癌症]]和[[艾滋病|艾滋病]]的患者的组织。2008年[[Warped巡回|Warped巡回]]期间，她用她的双乳做了一个模具，为{{le|保住乳房基金会|Keep A Breast Foundation}}筹集资金<ref>{{cite web |title=The Keep A Breast Foundation |url=http://www.keep-a-breast.org/breast-cast-art/history/ |accessdate=2014-05-20 |publisher=Keep A Breast Foundation |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330175940/http://keep-a-breast.org/breast-cast-art/history/ |archivedate=2014-03-30 }}</ref>。她还与[[邦妮·麦基|邦妮·麦基]]、[[凯茜·马斯格雷夫斯|凯茜·马斯格雷夫斯]]、[[莎拉·芭瑞黎丝|莎拉·芭瑞黎丝]]、[[艾丽·高登|艾丽·高登]]和二人组[[泰根与莎拉|泰根与莎拉]]主持并参演于2013年10月23日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶好莱坞碗（{{lang|en|Hollywood Bowl}}）举办的“我们能活下去”（{{lang|en|We Can Survive}}）演唱会。该演唱会的收益捐献给帮助身患[[乳腺癌|乳腺癌]]年轻女性的组织{{le|年轻人生存联盟|Young Survival Coalition}}<ref name="Hollywood Bowl">{{cite journal|last=Aguila|first=Justino|title=Katy Perry Hosts Famous Friends, Previews Next Tour at Hollywood Bowl: Live Review|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5770379/katy-perry-hosts-famous-friends-previews-next-tour-at-hollywood|magazine=Billboard|date=2013-10-24|accessdate=2014-04-28|journal=|archive-date=2014-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140624200053/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5770379/katy-perry-hosts-famous-friends-previews-next-tour-at-hollywood|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年6月，她为[[H&M|H&M]]的“时装抗击艾滋病”（{{lang|en|Fashion Against AIDS}}）活动设计了一件衣服，为艾滋病宣传项目筹集资金<ref>{{cite news|last=Vena|first=Jocelyn|title=Katy Perry, Tokio Hotel Join H&M for Fashion Against AIDS|url=http://newsroom.mtv.com/2009/05/06/katy-perry-tokio-hotel-join-hm-for-fashion-against-aids/|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2014-03-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090508092144/http://newsroom.mtv.com/2009/05/06/katy-perry-tokio-hotel-join-hm-for-fashion-against-aids/|archivedate=2009-05-08}}</ref>。

派瑞单曲《[[做自己_(单曲)|做自己]]》所得收益捐给了慈善机构{{le|MusiCares|MusiCares}}，以帮助处在艰难时期的音乐人<ref>{{cite news|title=Katy Perry donates proceeds from new single to charity|url=http://news.yahoo.com/katy-perry-donates-proceeds-single-charity-191441877.html|date=2012-02-16|publisher=Yahoo! News|accessdate=2014-05-25|first=Alexandra|last=Myers|archive-date=2014-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715030356/http://news.yahoo.com/katy-perry-donates-proceeds-single-charity-191441877.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在她的加州梦幻巡演中，她为“门票做慈善”（{{lang|en|Tickets-For-Charity}}）募捐活动筹集了17.5万美元。这些钱将由{{le|儿童健康基金会|Children's Health Fund}}（CHF）、慷慨水源（{{lang|en|Generosity Water}}）和{{le|美国人道主义协会|The Humane Society of the United States}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.childrenshealthfund.org/sites/default/files/Katy-Perry-TFC-Check-Presenation.pdf|title=Katy Perry Celebrates Over $175K Raised for Charity on Her California Dreams Tour through Tickets-for-Charity|publisher=Children's Health Fund|date=2011-12-08|accessdate=2014-04-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923202756/http://www.childrenshealthfund.org/sites/default/files/Katy-Perry-TFC-Check-Presenation.pdf|archivedate=2015-09-23}}</ref>三个慈善机构分得。27岁生日当天，派瑞为奥克兰的[[防止虐待动物协会|防止虐待动物协会]]设立捐赠页面<ref>{{cite web|title=Katy Perry Asks For Charity Donations To Mark Birthday|url=http://www.contactmusic.com/news/katy-perry-asks-for-charity-donations-to-mark-birthday_1252678|publisher=Contactmusic.com. Channel 4|date=2011-10-26|accessdate=2011-11-11|archive-date=2014-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102033332/http://www.contactmusic.com/news/katy-perry-asks-for-charity-donations-to-mark-birthday_1252678|dead-url=no}}</ref>，又在28岁生日时为{{le|大卫·林奇基金会|David Lynch Foundation}}设立了类似的页面<ref>{{cite web|last1=Davidson|first1=Danica|title=Sweet Treat: Katy Perry asks for Charitable Donations for her 28th Birthday|url=http://act.mtv.com/posts/sweet-tweet-katy-perry-donations-birthday/|publisher=MTV. Viacom|accessdate=2014-06-27|archive-date=2014-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102020105/http://act.mtv.com/posts/sweet-tweet-katy-perry-donations-birthday/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年3月29日，她与[[瑞安·西克雷斯特|瑞安·西克雷斯特]]、[[法瑞尔·威廉姆斯|法瑞尔·威廉姆斯]]、[[蒂姆·艾伦|蒂姆·艾伦]]、[[莉萨·埃德尔斯坦|莉萨·埃德尔斯坦]]和[[莱莉·基奥|莱莉·基奥]]为洛杉矶的[[洛杉矶当代艺术博物馆|当代艺术博物馆]]筹集240万美元<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6029354/katy-perry-pharrell-williams-help-raise-24-million-for-moca|first=Tina|last=Daunt|title=Katy Perry, Pharrell Williams Help Raise $2.4 Million for MOCA|magazine=Billboard|date=2014-03-31|accessdate=2014-04-10|journal=|archive-date=2014-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140403054200/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6029354/katy-perry-pharrell-williams-help-raise-24-million-for-moca|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 参与政治 ===
[[File:Katy_Perry_Hillary_Clinton,_I'm_With_Her_Concert.jpg|缩略图]]

派瑞是[[美国LGBT权益|同性恋权]]活动家。她{{le|石墙慈善组织|Stonewall (charity)}}的“今天会更好”（{{lang|en|It gets better......today}}）的预防同性恋欺凌运动期间支持该组织<ref>{{cite web|title=High profile support: Other messages|url=http://www.stonewall.org.uk/what_you_can_do/campaigning_opportunities/it_gets_better_today/4845.asp|publisher=Stonewall|date=2010-11-17|accessdate=2014-03-13|archive-date=2015-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414145258/http://www.stonewall.org.uk/what_you_can_do/campaigning_opportunities/it_gets_better_today/4845.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>，将她的歌曲《[[烟火_(歌曲)|烟火]]》的音乐录影带献给[[It_Gets_Better项目|It Gets Better项目]]<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/viral-videos/952410/katy-perry-dedicates-leaked-firework-video-to-lgbt-campaign|title=Katy Perry Dedicates Leaked 'Firework' Video to LGBT Campaign|magazine=Billboard|date=2010-10-28|first=Jillian|last=Mapes|accessdate=2014-04-28|journal=|archive-date=2015-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150719045440/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/viral-videos/952410/katy-perry-dedicates-leaked-firework-video-to-lgbt-campaign|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年10月，派瑞告诉{{le|做点什么|Do Something}}，她为成为一名同性恋活动家感到骄傲，表示“我一直是个很开放的人，但我绝对相信公平。”她证实她投票反对在法律上界定在加州结婚仅限于一位男性和一位女性结合的修正案《[[加利福尼亚州8号提案_(2008年)|8号提案]]》（最终裁定违宪）<ref name="DoSomething">{{cite web|url=http://www.dosomething.org/page/katy-perry-talks-about-gay-rights-interview-with-cgg|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006153308/https://www.dosomething.org/page/katy-perry-talks-about-gay-rights-interview-with-cgg|archivedate=2014-10-06|title=Katy Perry talks about gay rights in interview with CGG|publisher=Do Something|date=2008-11-04|accessdate=2011-11-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年6月，派瑞表达了她对同性恋平等的希望，评论道“我们将满怀希望地回首这一刻，想着我们现在要关心（其他）[[公民权利和政治权利|公民权]]问题。我们不可置信地摇着头，说着‘感谢上帝，我们进化了。’那会是我对未来的祈祷<ref>{{cite journal|last=Hauser|first=Brooke|title=Katy Perry Celebrates Her Independence|url=http://parade.condenast.com/31418/brookehauser/28-katy-perry-part-of-me/|magazine=Parade|date=2012-06-28|accessdate=2014-02-06|journal=|archive-date=2014-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221233214/http://parade.condenast.com/31418/brookehauser/28-katy-perry-part-of-me/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”2012年12月，{{le|特雷弗项目|The Trevor Project}}为表彰派瑞代表同性恋青少年所做的工作和行动，授予她特雷弗英雄奖（{{lang|en|Trevor Hero Award}}）<ref name="TrevorHero">{{cite web|title=Katy Perry Accepts Hero Award From Trevor Project|url=http://www.contactmusic.com/news/katy-perry-accepts-hero-award-from-trevor-project_3399852|publisher=Contactmusic.com|date=2012-12-03|accessdate=2014-04-28|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024081011/http://www.contactmusic.com/news/katy-perry-accepts-hero-award-from-trevor-project_3399852|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她自封为一位[[女权主义|女权主义者]]<ref>{{cite journal|last=Stampler|first=Laura|title=Katy Perry: Maybe I am a Feminist After All|url=http://time.com/28554/katy-perry-feminist-after-all-confused/|magazine=Time|date=2014-03-18|accessdate=2014-06-16|journal=|archive-date=2014-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615032440/http://time.com/28554/katy-perry-feminist-after-all-confused/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，于2013年4月亮相传播女性当权思想的“改变的钟声”（{{lang|en|Chime For Change}}）运动<ref>{{cite journal|title=Watch: Beyoncé, Blake Lively, Katy Perry, and More Unite in Chime for Change Video|url=http://www.elle.com/news/fashion-style/beyonce-blake-lively-katy-perry-chime-for-change-video|first=Lauren|last=Levinson|magazine=Elle|accessdate=2014-04-28|date=2013-04-16|journal=|archive-date=2014-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630135325/http://www.elle.com/news/fashion-style/beyonce-blake-lively-katy-perry-chime-for-change-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她还表示，美国缺乏[[美国医疗系统|免费医疗]]把她“彻底搞疯”<ref>{{cite journal|title=Katy Perry Talks Body Image, Fame, and Politics in Rolling Stone Cover Story|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/katy-perry-talks-body-image-fame-and-politics-in-rolling-stone-cover-story-20110622|magazine=Rolling Stone|date=2011-06-22|accessdate=2014-02-16|journal=|archive-date=2014-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307074611/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/katy-perry-talks-body-image-fame-and-politics-in-rolling-stone-cover-story-20110622|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

透过[[Twitter|Twitter]]和出席他的集会，派瑞支持总统[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]竞选连任，并称赞他对[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]<ref name=bamanails>{{cite news|last=Porter|first=Amber|title=Katy Perry Nails it for Obama|url=http://abcnews.go.com/blogs/politics/2012/10/katy-perry-nails-it-for-obama/|date=2012-10-08|publisher=ABC News|accessdate=2012-11-04|archive-date=2012-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012020542/http://abcnews.go.com/blogs/politics/2012/10/katy-perry-nails-it-for-obama/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和平等权的支持<ref>{{cite journal|last=Strecker|first=Erin|title=Katy Perry performing another free concert at Obama rally|url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2012/11/01/katy-perry-milwaukee-president-obama/|magazine=Entertainment Weekly|date=2012-11-01|accessdate=2012-11-04|journal=|archive-date=2014-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140205082103/http://music-mix.ew.com/2012/11/01/katy-perry-milwaukee-president-obama/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。她在于洛杉矶、拉斯维加斯和威斯康星州的三次集会上奥巴马表演，演唱《{{le|让我们在一起|Let's Stay Together (song)|Let's Stay Together}}》和她的一些歌曲。在拉斯维加斯表演时，她穿着一条用选票复印本做的连衣裙，套上了奥巴马的票箱<ref>{{cite journal|last=Strecker|first=Erin|title=Katy Perry performs at third President Obama rally in Wisconsin|url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2012/11/01/katy-perry-milwaukee-president-obama/|magazine=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=2014-02-09|journal=|archive-date=2014-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140205082103/http://music-mix.ew.com/2012/11/01/katy-perry-milwaukee-president-obama/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在Twitter上，她鼓励歌迷投票给奥巴马。2013年8月，派瑞批评[[澳大利亚总理|澳大利亚总理]]候选人[[托尼·阿博特|托尼·阿博特]]，由于他反对同性婚姻。她告诉阿博特，“我爱身为人类的你，但我不会把票投给你<ref name="TonyAbbott">{{cite news|title=Katy Perry confronts Tony Abbott on gay marriage|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/australiaandthepacific/australia/10243985/Katy-Perry-confronts-Tony-Abbott-on-gay-marriage.html|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2014-02-06|date=2013-08-15|archive-date=2014-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322153911/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/australiaandthepacific/australia/10243985/Katy-Perry-confronts-Tony-Abbott-on-gay-marriage.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”2014年4月，她公开出席了[[玛丽安娜·威廉森|玛丽安娜·威廉森]]的{{le|加利福尼亚州第33国会选区|California's 33rd congressional district}}竞选活动政治新闻发布会，公开表示支持玛丽安娜<ref>{{cite journal|last=Schwiegershausen|first=Erica|title=Katy Perry Exposed a Springy Strip of Upper Belly|url=http://nymag.com/thecut/2014/04/katy-perry-exposed-a-springy-strip-of-belly.html|magazine=New York|accessdate=2014-04-09|date=2014-04-09|journal=|archive-date=2014-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140411161354/http://nymag.com/thecut/2014/04/katy-perry-exposed-a-springy-strip-of-belly.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派瑞也欢迎前[[美国国务卿|国务卿]][[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]参加[[2016年美国总统选举|2016年总统竞选]]<ref>{{Cite web|title = Katy Perry writes new theme song for Hillary Clinton 2016 Presidential campaign|url = http://www.axs.com/news/katy-perry-writes-new-theme-song-for-hillary-clinton-2016-presidential-33291|accessdate = 2015-08-21|archive-date = 2015-09-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150906220707/http://www.axs.com/news/katy-perry-writes-new-theme-song-for-hillary-clinton-2016-presidential-33291|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Celebs show they are ready for Hillary by embracing her logo|url = http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/celebs-show-they-are-ready-hillary-embracing-her-logo|accessdate = 2015-08-21|archive-date = 2015-08-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150816132122/http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/celebs-show-they-are-ready-hillary-embracing-her-logo|dead-url = no}}</ref>，并为希拉里竞选捐了2700美元<ref>{{Cite web|title = Page By Page Report Display For 201510159003054880|page = 14954|url = http://docquery.fec.gov/cgi-bin/fecimg/?201510159003069833|publisher = Federal Election Commission|accessdate = 2015-10-25|archive-date = 2015-11-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151117030440/http://docquery.fec.gov/cgi-bin/fecimg/?201510159003069833|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2015年10月，她在爱荷华州为克林顿的集会表演<ref>{{cite news|title=Katy Perry to Rally Hillary Clinton Supporters in Iowa|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6722944/katy-perry-hillary-clinton-iowa-rally|accessdate=2016-06-03|work=Billboard|date=2015-10-10|archive-date=2016-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160515112252/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6722944/katy-perry-hillary-clinton-iowa-rally|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2016年3月与[[埃尔顿·约翰|埃尔顿·约翰]]出席克林顿纽约筹款音乐会<ref>{{cite news|last1=Claiborne|first1=Matthew|title=Katy Perry, Elton John Perform at Hillary Clinton Fundraiser In New York|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/katy-perry-elton-john-perform-hillary-clinton-fundraiser/story?id=37359679|accessdate=2016-06-03|publisher=ABC News|date=2016-03-03|archive-date=2016-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610093149/http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/katy-perry-elton-john-perform-hillary-clinton-fundraiser/story?id=37359679|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[2016年民主党全国代表大会|2016年民主党全国代表大会]]上，凯蒂为希拉蕊·克林顿站台并献唱。她鼓励民众投票给希拉蕊，并评论称他们在竞选期间会“像[[美国來福枪协会|美国來福枪协会]]的[[遊說|说客]]一样强大”，“像任何百万富翁那样的有说服力”<ref>{{cite journal|last=Grant|first=Sarah|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/politics/news/watch-katy-perry-rise-and-roar-for-hillary-clinton-at-dnc-w431537|title=Watch Katy Perry 'Rise' and 'Roar' for Hillary Clinton at DNC|journal=Rolling Stone|date=2016-07-28|accessdate=2016-07-29|archive-date=2016-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160730152403/http://www.rollingstone.com/politics/news/watch-katy-perry-rise-and-roar-for-hillary-clinton-at-dnc-w431537|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

